{"type":"message","id":"034b2b94","parentId":"3968010e","timestamp":"2026-05-15T23:26:57.845Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, I've saved the location. Now let me confirm with the owner what he wants to do next - use Auto.js to automatically clock in when he arrives at this location?","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"位置收到，已记录 ✅\n\n梅陇四村（121.421920, 31.138598）我存好了。\n\n现在接下去就是真正的自动化打卡了——你手机 **Android 还是 iOS**？如果是 Android 我可以直接给你写个 Auto.js 脚本，到了这个位置自动帮你打卡。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":254,"output":102,"cacheRead":20864,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21220,"cost":{"input":0.000035560000000000005,"output":0.00002856,"cacheRead":0.000584192,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000648312}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778887616312,"responseId":"22f47df0-9b52-4528-8b0a-5467f7cb127c"}}
