{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6f4ef04124a0b3f88bbf1ff7322\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yousan(叶枝君)\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-05-16 07:27 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yousan(叶枝君) (ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"name\": \"Yousan(叶枝君)\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"e7ff8995","parentId":"7fe2253d","timestamp":"2026-05-15T23:27:40.783Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"8859a2d8","parentId":"e7ff8995","timestamp":"2026-05-15T23:27:47.045Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"主人想让我在 PC 端的安卓模拟器上打卡，用他的定位。这个思路有点意思——在模拟器上伪装成手机打卡。\n\n让我想想可行性：\n\n1. **原理**：PC 安卓模拟器（比如 MuMu、BlueStacks、LDPlayer）本身可以装飞书，也可以模拟 GPS 位置\n2. **核心问题**：飞书打卡会校验真实位置，模拟器的 GPS 模拟可能被飞书识破\n3. **另一个问题**：飞书打卡是否依赖其他手机硬件特征（IMEI、设备指纹等）来防止模拟器打卡？\n\n让我给主人分析一下可行性，然后问他要不要试试看。\n\n实际上，技术上是可行的：\n1. 在模拟器里装飞书\n2. 用模拟器的 GPS 模拟功能设置定位到梅陇四村\n3. 用 Auto.js 或者 ADB 自动化点击打卡\n\n但有几个风险：\n- 飞书可能检测模拟器环境，拒绝打卡\n- 可能被判定为作弊打卡\n- 公司考勤管理那边可能有问题\n\n不过主人问的是\"能不能\"，技术上回答应该是\"能，但有限制\"。我应该先问问他在用什么模拟器，然后看看能不能帮他实现。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"有意思的思路 🤔 技术上可行，但有几个坑得先确定。\n\n**技术原理：**\nPC 安卓模拟器（MuMu/雷电/蓝叠）可以：\n1. ✅ **装飞书** — 完全没问题\n2. ✅ **模拟 GPS 定位** — 模拟器自带模拟定位功能，设成梅陇四村的坐标\n3. ✅ **自动化点击** — ADB / Auto.js 写脚本模拟点击打卡按钮\n\n**但有几个致命问题：**\n\n| 问题 | 风险 |\n|------|------|\n| 🚩 **飞书检测模拟器** | 飞书考勤模块会检测设备环境，很多公司直接禁止模拟器打卡 |\n| 🚩 **设备指纹** | 飞书能识别模拟器的 IMEI、设备 ID 等特征，跟真机不同 |\n| 🚩 **GPS 模拟 vs 真实 GPS** | 模拟器提供的伪 GPS 精度和特征跟真实硬件不一样，飞书后台可能识别 |\n| 🚩 **合规问题** | 伪造打卡属于考勤舞弊，被发现后果挺严重的 |\n\n**如果你还是想试一下：**\n\n告诉我你现在用的模拟器（MuMu / 雷电 / 蓝叠？），我可以帮你：\n1. 写个 Auto.js 脚本 + ADB 方案\n2. 设置模拟 GPS 到梅陇四村\n3. 自动化打卡\n\n但说真的，**如果公司查得严，建议还是用手真机打卡**。模拟器打卡当\"万一迟到了救急用\"还行，不要当常规方案用 😅"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":14019,"output":595,"cacheRead":7296,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21910,"cost":{"input":0.00196266,"output":0.0001666,"cacheRead":0.000204288,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002333548}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778887660783,"responseId":"fa93b0fd-afbd-4aa6-b494-f4f3695a8b03"}}
{"type":"message","id":"d22a830d","parentId":"8859a2d8","timestamp":"2026-05-15T23:29:34.788Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[message_id: om_x100b6f4e8b6c04a0b283d46f102b237]\nYousan(叶枝君): 我想实现电子围栏功能，有没可能自己写个应用来实时获取定位，再用飞书打卡呢"}],"timestamp":1778887774787}}
{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6f4e8b6c04a0b283d46f102b237\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yousan(叶枝君)\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-05-16 07:29 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yousan(叶枝君) (ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"name\": \"Yousan(叶枝君)\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"a67ec2da","parentId":"d22a830d","timestamp":"2026-05-15T23:29:34.789Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"ee637231","parentId":"a67ec2da","timestamp":"2026-05-15T23:29:45.102Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The owner wants to implement a geofencing solution - write a custom app that monitors GPS location in real-time and automatically clocks in via Feishu when entering the geofence area (梅陇四村).\n\nLet me think about the feasibility:\n\n1. **Real-time GPS monitoring** - Easy. Android app with location service / foreground service\n2. **Feishu punch-in automation** - This is the hard part. Feishu doesn't have an open API for clock-in/punch-card. So we'd need accessibility service (Android) to simulate taps on the Feishu app.\n\nSo the architecture would be:\n- An Android app running on his phone (or a dedicated Android device)\n- GPS background service with geofencing\n- When entering the geofence -> trigger Feishu auto-punch via Accessibility Service\n\nOr alternatively:\n- Run the Android app on a PC Android emulator (as he mentioned wanting to use the emulator)\n- Set emulated GPS to his home location\n- Use ADB + accessibility to punch in\n\nLet me think about what's the cleanest path:\n\n**Pure Android app approach:**\n- Write a simple Android app that:\n  1. Runs a foreground service with GPS\n  2. Defines geofence for 梅陇四村\n  3. When entering geofence, launches Feishu and uses AccessibilityService to navigate to the punch page and tap the punch button\n- This is basically Auto.js in app form, but more customized\n\n**Alternative: Use Auto.js directly**\n- Install Auto.js on the phone\n- Write a script that:\n  1. Watches GPS/location\n  2. Geo-fence trigger\n  3. Opens Feishu and simulates tap on the punch button\n- Much simpler than building a full app\n\n**问题：**\n飞书打卡能不能靠无障碍服务点？可以，只要找到打卡按钮的控件 ID 或坐标。\n\n实际上，主人问的是「自己写个应用来实时获取定位，再用飞书打卡」——他的意思是两个独立的东西：一个定位监控应用 + 飞书打卡。\n\n但关键点还是：**飞书没有开放打卡 API**，所以任何自动化方案都绕不开无障碍服务模拟点击。\n\n让我给主人一个明确的技术方案选择。\n\n方案1：Auto.js（最快最省事）\n方案2：自己写个 Android App（定制化更强）\n方案3：用 Tasker + 飞书快捷方式（轻度方案）\n\n我需要确认他是不是想用真机做，还是坚持模拟器路线。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"可以的，思路完全对 👍 我来拆一下可行性：\n\n---\n\n## 技术路线\n\n飞书**没有开放打卡 API**，所以绕不开「无障碍服务模拟点击」。架构就是：\n\n```\nGPS 监听 → 进入围栏 → 打开飞书 → 用无障碍服务自动点打卡按钮\n```\n\n## 可选方案\n\n### 🥇 方案一：Auto.js（最快，推荐）\n不用自己写应用，装个 **Auto.js**（开源免费）就跑起来了。\n\n**脚本逻辑：**\n```\n1. 后台监听 GPS\n2. 进入梅陇四村围栏（半径 ~200m）\n3. 自动打开飞书 → 考勤 → 打卡按钮\n4. 打完即退\n```\n\n代码量大概就 **几十行 JavaScript**，我直接帮你写。\n\n### 🥈 方案二：自己写 Android 原生 App\n用 Kotlin/Java 写一个：\n- `ForegroundService` 处理后台定位\n- `GeofencingClient` 定义电子围栏\n- `AccessibilityService` 操作飞书打卡\n- 可以加 Wifi SSID 二次确认，避免路过误触\n\n**优点：** 完全自主可控，可上架到自己的设备\n**缺点：** 开发周期长（签名、编译、适配 Android 版本）\n\n### 🥉 方案三：纯 Tasker（不写代码）\n用 Tasker 搭积木：\n- Profile: Location → 进入梅陇四村范围\n- Task: 打开飞书 → 模拟点击打卡\n- 不需要写一行代码\n\n---\n\n**先确认几个事情：**\n1. 你用什么手机？**Android 还是 iOS？**\n2. 是真机跑还是坚持在**模拟器**上跑？\n3. **飞书打卡流程长啥样？** — 截个图/说下你打卡要几步（打开飞书 → 工作台 → 考勤 → 打卡？还是直接有个快捷入口？）\n\n知道这几样我直接给你把方案定了写出来 😎"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":14421,"output":965,"cacheRead":7296,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22682,"cost":{"input":0.0020189400000000003,"output":0.0002702,"cacheRead":0.000204288,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0024934280000000002}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778887774790,"responseId":"416ffd77-2ee8-4891-9066-4bfd8e4b885f"}}
