{"type":"message","id":"a2ad4e3a","parentId":"9f756a4e","timestamp":"2026-05-15T23:41:55.342Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"主人想继续昨天的 TAPD 自动提单流程。让我查一下 MEMORY.md 里关于 TAPD 的记录，还有相关的 skill 文件。\n\n从 MEMORY.md 我看到：\n- TAPD 自动提单进行中\n- Playwright 已安装 v1.60.0\n- WAF 已绕过，成功加载 TAPD 登录页\n- 微信扫码登录二维码已显示\n- 待完成：扫码登录后走通提单流程\n\n我需要先看看 TAPD skill 的配置，然后继续这个流程。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_oj2aiGbqujeedk0o33NH7795","name":"memory_search","arguments":{"query":"TAPD 自动提单 自动提需求 流程","corpus":"memory"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_01_2MKZRxPT3QfX5BITYuqN3075","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls ~/.openclaw/plugin-skills/tapd-bug-create/ 2>$null"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1162,"output":238,"cacheRead":21376,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22776,"cost":{"input":0.00016268,"output":0.00006664,"cacheRead":0.000598528,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000827848}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778888513193,"responseId":"5430d381-36bf-4b26-b035-0f032d3eb182"}}
{"type":"message","id":"09e527f2","parentId":"a2ad4e3a","timestamp":"2026-05-15T23:41:56.322Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_oj2aiGbqujeedk0o33NH7795","toolName":"memory_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"b9e2b66db94a2aa0f71209d3753cde90c6f719af77c7746856e86fa4536d6af7\",\n      \"path\": \"MEMORY.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 28,\n      \"endLine\": 55,\n      \"score\": 0.9536614284341813,\n      \"textScore\": 0.32099476176751457,\n      \"snippet\": \"登录后保存 Cookie，后续分析提单页面结构（bug/需求表单字段）。\\n\\n## 同事白名单\\n\\n- **主人 Yousan(叶枝君)** `ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f` — 无限制\\n- **允许同事执行的任务：** 更新测试服、提单（TAPD 自动创建缺陷）\\n\\n## 群组信息\\n\\n- **月圆之夜CCG开发群** → `oc_59afc01122ec0cd04ca4d8c5103c7a77`\\n  - 兵王(周以天) open_id：`ou_348eeddd81d4c03865f9f1684fce6966`\\n  - 小骑士(谭佳钦) open_id：`ou_fc5144301797fb813a1fee33e1130ac3`\\n\\n## 飞书消息 @ 人规范\\n- 正确格式：`<at user_id=\\\"open_id\\\">显示名字</at>`\\n- 飞书按 user_id 解析显示名，`<at>` 内的名字只是兜底文本\\n\\n## TAPD 自动提单 Skill\\n- Skill 路径：`~/.openclaw/plugin-skills/tapd-bug-create/`\\n- 工作区 ID：`31253609`（月圆之夜）\\n- 创建缺陷 URL：`/31253609/bugtrace/bugs/add`\\n- 创建需求 URL：`/31253609/prong/stories/add`\\n- 模板 ID：`1131253609001000011`\\n- 用户 ID：叶枝君=`1415287364`，周以天=`1166740146`，谭佳钦=`553342158\\n\\nSource: MEMORY.md#L28-L55\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"MEMORY.md#L28-L55\",\n      \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"e22a3dde04cf06bb9262130cf91f31cdf7923ef95e0604bbd16e4543a5f40821\",\n      \"path\": \"memory/2026-05-15.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 123,\n      \"endLine\": 147,\n      \"score\": 0.9504859608028331,\n      \"textScore\": 0.3178543818554647,\n      \"snippet\": \"| 优先级 | `data[Bug][priority]` | P0/P1/P2/P3 |\\n| 研发分支 | `data[Bug][custom_field_one]` | #BugCustomFieldOne |\\n| 模块 | `data[Bug][module]` | #BugModule |\\n| 描述 | `data[Bug][description]` | #BugDescription(hidden textarea) |\\n| template_id | `data[template_id]` | 1131253609001000011 |\\n\\n### TAPD Bug 默认分配规则\\n- 程序→叶枝君、策划→赵乾、UI→小冰、特效→肖和\\n- 抄送人默认：周以天（兵王）\\n\\n### TAPD Skill 创建\\n- Skill 路径：`~/.openclaw/plugin-skills/tapd-bug-create/`\\n- 包含 SKILL.md + scripts/create_bug.mjs + references/bug-fields.md + references/tapd-login.md\\n- 工作区 ID：31253609（月圆之夜）\\n- 模板 ID：1131253609001000011\\n- 用户 ID：叶枝君=1415287364，周以天=1166740146，谭佳钦=553342158\\n\\n### 同事白名单\\n- 允许任务：更新测试服、提单（TAPD 自动创建缺陷）\\n- 白名单文件：`COLLEAGUE_WHITELIST.md`\\n\\n### 遇到的问题\\n-\\n\\nSource: memory/2026-05-15.md#L123-L147\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/2026-05-15.md#L123-L147\",\n      \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"673796f98d758555187ce5fd77af8b32bb4d83338996a4fbe64bba6608371ab4\",\n      \"path\": \"MEMORY.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 1,\n      \"endLine\": 36,\n      \"score\": 0.9477130404419274,\n      \"textScore\": 0.31553912739844914,\n      \"snippet\": \"# MEMORY.md\\n\\n## 热更流水线配置（2026-05-15）\\n\\n### 执行方式\\n- **入口：** `RunBuildPipelineHotUpdate.bat`\\n- **Unity 路径：** `C:\\\\Program Files\\\\Unity\\\\Hub\\\\Editor\\\\2020.3.49f1\\\\Editor\\\\Unity.exe`\\n- **入口方法：** `YYZY.BuildPipeline.BuildPipeline.RunHotUpdatePipeline`\\n- **默认增量构建**（不清 Bundles 缓存，速度快。仅资源丢失或异常时才全量）\\n\\n### 更新测试服流程\\n1. 检查是否有 Unity 进程在执行 `RunHotUpdatePipeline`\\n2. 关掉所有 Unity Editor 进程\\n3. Git pull\\n4. 运行 RunBuildPipelineHotUpdate.bat\\n5. 完成后在「月圆之夜CCG开发群」`oc_59afc01122ec0cd04ca4d8c5103c7a77` @兵王 `ou_348eeddd81d4c03865f9f1684fce6966` 通知\\n\\n## TAPD 自动提单（进行中 - 2026-05-15）\\n\\n### 进度\\n- ✅ Playwright 已安装（v1.60.0）\\n- ✅ WAF 已绕过，成功加载 TAPD 登录页（`cloud_logins/login`）\\n- ✅ 微信扫码二维码已显示（`mp.weixin.qq.com`）\\n- ⏳ **待完成：** 扫码登录后走通提单流程\\n\\n### 登录方式选择\\n\\nSource: MEMORY.md#L1-L36\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"MEMORY.md#L1-L36\",\n      \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"77e6b9cdc7938a79b49bf6468fe630fb0ae2ff88729ef286837bd4de560415b3\",\n      \"path\": \"memory/2026-05-15.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 79,\n      