{"type":"message","id":"5f678eae","parentId":"f0cf26b7","timestamp":"2026-05-15T23:41:59.488Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_0FeBp7dAtRFJtMq9EJJp4091","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: tapd-bug-create\ndescription: Create bug tickets on TAPD (腾讯敏捷产品研发平台) for the 月圆之夜 project via Playwright browser automation. \n  Use when user says: create a bug, file a bug, report a bug, 提单, 提bug, 创建缺陷, create a story/requirement.\n  Also handles TAPD login, cookie management, and default assignment rules.\n---\n\n# TAPD Bug & Story Create\n\nAutomate creating work items on TAPD for workspace `31253609` (月圆之夜).\n\n## Prerequisites\n\n- **Cookies** in `workspace/tapd_cookies.json` (owner: 枝君, workspace 31253609 accessible)\n- **Playwright** v1.60.0+\n- **WAF Bypass**: Use provided stealth init script; fallback to `headless: false` if blocked\n\n## Quick Start - Create a Bug\n\n```javascript\nimport { createBug } from './scripts/create_bug.mjs';\nconst url = await createBug({\n  title: 'Bug title',\n  handler: '谭佳钦;',     // 格式: 姓名; 不要填ID\n  cc: '周以天;',           // 默认兵王\n  priority: 'P2',\n  version: '【1V1】正式版本V2.0',\n  module: '1V1',\n  branch: 'YZY_1V1 V1.0 Beta',\n  description: 'Description',\n});\n// Returns: https://www.tapd.cn/tapd_fe/31253609/bug/detail/{id}\n```\n\n## Default Assignment Rules\n\n| Bug 类型 | 处理人 | 抄送人 |\n|----------|--------|--------|\n| 程序 (Code) | `叶枝君;` | `周以天;` |\n| 策划 (Design) | `赵乾;` | `周以天;` |\n| UI | `小冰;` | `周以天;` |\n| 特效 (Effect) | `肖和;` | `周以天;` |\n\n**所有 bug 单抄送人默认加兵王（周以天）**\n\n## Set Handler/CC - Autocomplete (IMPORTANT)\n\nThe handler and CC fields use TAPD's user autocomplete. **Do NOT set hidden fields directly** (will show as ID).\n\nCorrect approach (type name + press Enter):\n```javascript\nawait page.type('#BugCurrentOwnerValue', '谭佳钦', {delay: 100});\nawait page.waitForTimeout(2000);\nawait page.keyboard.press('Enter');\n// This triggers TAPD's autocomplete and properly resolves the user\n```\n\n## Create a Story (Requirement)\n\n```javascript\n// URL: https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/prong/stories/add\nawait page.fill('#StoryName', 'Story title');\nawait page.selectOption('#StoryPriority', 'P1');\n// Submit requires dynamically creating a submit input:\nawait page.evaluate(() => {\n  const form = document.querySelector('form');\n  const btn = document.createElement('input');\n  btn.type = 'submit';\n  btn.name = 'data[save_return]';\n  btn.value = '提交&返回';\n  form.appendChild(btn);\n  btn.click();\n});\n```\n\n## Create a Sub-Story\n\nSet the parent story ID in the \"父需求\" search field, or set `data[Story][parent_id]` hidden field to the parent story's ID.\n\n## Key Configuration\n\n| Setting | Value |\n|---------|-------|\n| Workspace ID | `31253609` |\n| Bug template ID | `1131253609001000011` |\n| Story templated ID | `1131253609001000047` |\n| Bug create URL | `/31253609/bugtrace/bugs/add` |\n| Bug edit URL | `/31253609/bugtrace/bugs/edit?id={bugId}` |\n| Story create URL | `/31253609/prong/stories/add` |\n| Submit (return) | `#save_return` (name=`data[save_return]`, value=`提交&返回`) |\n| Submit (view) | `#save_view` (name=`data[submit]`, value=`提交&查看`) |\n| Cookies file | `workspace/tapd_cookies.json` |\n| User IDs | 叶枝君=1415287364, 周以天=1166740146, 谭佳钦=553342158 |\n\n## Bug Fields\n\nSee `references/bug-fields.md` for all available fields, accepted values, and the default template.\n\n## Anti-WAF Measures\n\n1. **Headless mode** (preferred): Apply the full stealth init script:\n   - Delete `navigator.webdriver`\n   - Override: plugins, languages, hardwareConcurrency\n   - Add `window.chrome` object\n   - Use real Chrome UA\n2. **Headed mode** (fallback): `headless: false` — always works, no WAF issues\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778888519488}}
{"type":"message","id":"f701d514","parentId":"5f678eae","timestamp":"2026-05-15T23:41:59.488Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_01_HYsFEWO5HOTMNxryMQlx2764","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"从 BuildPipelineConfig.bytes 二进制解析到的参数值：\n- 打资源版本 string: \"1.0.44\"（也有可能是空串走默认值）\n- CDN 根目录 string: \"D:/cdn_solo\"\n- CDN 版本 string: 各渠道独立配置\n\n### TAPD自动登录进度\n- ✅ Playwright 1.60.0 已安装\n- ✅ WAF绕过成功（anti-detection脚本 + 模拟真实浏览器 fingerprint）\n- ✅ 微信扫码页面已打开（mp.weixin.qq.com）\n- ⏳ 等待主人扫码登录后继续提单流程\n\n### 更新测试服记录\n- 第1次：失败 — YooAsset 差异资源包检测失败（增量构建验证不通过）\n- 第2次：失败 — 同上原因\n- 第3次：成功 — 清理Bundles缓存后全量构建通过\n- 第4次：成功 — 增量构建，CDN上传降级为本地模式（D:/cdn_solo非git仓库）\n- 后续使用**增量构建**模式，不清理Bundles缓存\n\n## TAPD 自动提单系统（完整搭建）\n\n### TAPD 登录（Cookie 方式）\n- 最终使用主人的 Chrome 浏览器手动登录后提取 Cookie\n- Cookie 已保存到 `workspace/tapd_cookies.json`\n- Storage state 已保存到 `workspace/tapd_storage.json`\n- 登录用户：枝君（workspace 31253609 可访问）\n- 备用：邮箱/密码登录、手机号+验证码、微信扫码\n\n### TAPD API 关键发现\n- 查询 Bug 列表：`POST /api/aggregation/bug_aggregation/get_bugs_list`\n- 查询 Bug 详情：`POST /api/aggregation/workitem_aggregation/common_get_info`\n- 创建 Bug 页面：`/31253609/bugtrace/bugs/add`\n- 创建 Story 页面：`/31253609/prong/stories/add`\n- 编辑 Bug 页面：`/31253609/bugtrace/bugs/edit?id={bugId}`\n- CSRF token cookie：`dsc-token`\n- 提交按钮：`#save_return`（提交&返回）、`#save_view`（提交&查看）\n\n### Bug 字段表\n| 字段 | 表单 name | 规则 |\n|------|-----------|------|\n| 标题 | `data[Bug][title]` | #BugTitle，必填 |\n| 发现版本 | `data[Bug][version_report]` | #BugVersionReport，必填 |\n| 处理人 | `data[Bug][current_owner]` | #BugCurrentOwner(hidden)，格式：`姓名;` |\n| 处理人显示 | (none) | #BugCurrentOwnerValue，填姓名触发自动补全 |\n| 抄送人 | `data[Bug][cc]` | #BugCc(hidden)，默认加兵王 |\n| 优先级 | `data[Bug][priority]` | P0/P1/P2/P3 |\n| 研发分支 | `data[Bug][custom_field_one]` | #BugCustomFieldOne |\n| 模块 | `data[Bug][module]` | #BugModule |\n| 描述 | `data[Bug][description]` | #BugDescription(hidden textarea) |\n| template_id | `data[template_id]` | 1131253609001000011 |\n\n### TAPD Bug 默认分配规则\n- 程序→叶枝君、策划→赵乾、UI→小冰、特效→肖和\n- 抄送人默认：周以天（兵王）\n\n### TAPD Skill 创建\n- Skill 路径：`~/.openclaw/plugin-skills/tapd-bug-create/`\n- 包含 SKILL.md + scripts/create_bug.mjs + references/bug-fields.md + references/tapd-login.md\n- 工作区 ID：31253609（月圆之夜）\n- 模板 ID：1131253609001000011\n- 用户 ID：叶枝君=1415287364，周以天=1166740146，谭佳钦=553342158\n\n### 同事白名单\n- 允许任务：更新测试服、提单（TAPD 自动创建缺陷）\n- 白名单文件：`COLLEAGUE_WHITELIST.md`\n\n### 遇到的问题\n- Bug 编辑页保存失败（保存按钮隐藏不可见，submit input 无法触发 AJAX 保存）\n- 处理人自动补全在编辑页不弹出下拉菜单（但在创建页工作正常）\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778888519488}}
{"type":"message","id":"2cb7331e","parentId":"f701d514","timestamp":"2026-05-15T23:42:02.522Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Okay, so the TAPD auto-bug-creation system is quite well set up already. Let me check:\n\n1. Cookies are saved (`tapd_cookies.json`)\n2. Storage state is saved (`tapd_storage.json`)\n3. The SKILL.md has been created with the full workflow\n4. The create_bug.mjs script exists\n\nLet me check what scripts are available and what state the cookies/storage are in. The user said \"继续昨天的自动提需求单流程\" - which means \"continue yesterday's auto-requirement-submission flow\". \n\nWait, the user said \"自动提需求单流程\" not \"提 bug 流程\". The difference is:\n- **提需求 (Story/Requirement)** - 需求单\n- **提 Bug (Bug)** - 缺陷\n\nLet me check the scripts directory to see what's available, and also check if the cookies are still valid.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，让我看看当前脚本和 Cookie 的状况。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_ZPDWk9MUOyNrFQMqGT7r9363","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\plugin-skills\\tapd-bug-create\\scripts\\"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_01_7PMDMrLhWJvXVth3zxzX9897","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\plugin-skills\\tapd-bug-create\\references\\"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_02_43sVGEJA7aln82k0vAoR0032","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\tapd_cookies.json 2>$null; ls C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\tapd_storage.json 2>$null"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":2187,"output":403,"cacheRead":25856,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":28446,"cost":{"input":0.00030618,"output":0.00011284000000000001,"cacheRead":0.000723968,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001142988}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778888519489,"responseId":"cdc5cfc3-c2f0-4ac2-8fcf-47b1fa74bb0c"}}
