{"type":"message","id":"7b05f088","parentId":"da1b2cbe","timestamp":"2026-05-16T02:55:29.303Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Image analysis failed. Let me describe what I might need to do based on the textual information provided.\n\nThe user says: \"玩家反馈咒语突破对月圆之夜无效\" — Player reports that \"咒语突破\" (a card/ability called \"Spell Breakthrough\") has no effect against \"月圆之夜\".\n\nIn the context of their game \"月圆之夜\" (Night of the Full Moon), this sounds like a bug report about the \"咒语突破\" card/effect not working properly against what may be a card called \"月圆之夜\" or the \"月圆之夜\" version/mode.\n\nWait, actually in the context of the game \"月圆之夜\" (Night of the Full Moon), \"月圆之夜\" could refer to the game name itself, or it could be a card in the game. Looking at the screenshots might help clarify.\n\nSince I can't view the images, let me try a different approach. But the user is the sender (Yousan/叶枝君), so they trust me with this info.\n\nLet me just ask about the details or proceed with what I know.\n\nActually, looking at the card name \"咒语突破\" and \"月圆之夜\" - in the game 月圆之夜 (Night of the Full Moon) which is a card game, \"咒语突破\" is likely a card or ability, and \"月圆之夜\" could be a specific character (月圆之夜版本的主角) or a game mode.\n\nActually, in the context of Night of the Full Moon game mechanics, \"月圆之夜\" is the name of the game itself. So the bug is about the \"咒语突破\" (Spell Breakthrough) feature/card not working in the game.\n\nWait, but that doesn't quite make sense either. Let me think... In card games, \"咒语突破\" could be a card that \"breaks through spells\" - maybe it's a card that should negate/dispel something but doesn't work against certain targets.\n\nI could try the image with a different approach. Or I could just ask the user for more details.\n\nActually, let me try reading the images differently or just proceed with what information I have. The user said \"玩家反馈咒语突破对月圆之夜无效\" and sent 2 screenshots.\n\nSince I