{"type":"message","id":"838a1ef9","parentId":"ec0f0bda","timestamp":"2026-05-16T02:57:18.429Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK several issues:\n\n1. **Handler \"西奥\"** - not found in autocomplete. I need to check who this person is. Let me look at the screenshot to see what the page looks like.\n\n2. **Attachments** - couldn't find upload input. The file upload widget in TAPD is likely not a simple `<input type=\"file\">` - it might be a button that triggers a file dialog. Let me check the screenshot.\n\n3. **Submit button `#save_return`** - it exists but it's `display: none` (class `display-none`). The submit button in TAPD is hidden and triggered by a visible anchor/link instead. Looking at the bug-fields.md, it mentions clicking `#_view` first which triggers the save_return.\n\nLet me look at the screenshot and also check the TAPD create_bug.mjs script - it used `await page.click('#_view');` not `#save_return`.\n\nLet me re-read the create_bug.mjs:\n```javascript\n// Submit - click the visible anchor button\nawait page.waitForTimeout(500);\nawait page.click('#_view');\n```\n\nSo the correct button to click is `#_view` (a visible anchor that triggers the hidden submit). Let me fix the script.\n\nAlso, I need to figure out who 西奥 is. Let me check the screenshot and also search the existing bug-fields.md - I don't see 西奥 in the user list. Let me search the workspace for this name.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"几个问题需要修。先看看截图了解页面结构。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_cw6RScdxt9op99eGsjuS0616","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Set-Location C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace; Test-Path bug_form_before_submit.png"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":548,"output":400,"cacheRead":39680,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":40628,"cost":{"input":0.00007672000000000001,"output":0.00011200000000000001,"cacheRead":0.00111104,"cacheWrite