{"type":"message","id":"6e21a757","parentId":"796e07b3","timestamp":"2026-05-16T03:41:09.568Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Wait, I keep writing headed-mode scripts with long waits. Let me think about this differently.\n\nThe user wants to delete one of the two identical bugs. I know TAPD's API well enough from the research. Let me try to find a more efficient way.\n\nActually, the simplest approach might be to just open the bug edit page and look for a delete button there. The TAPD bug edit page URL has the format: `https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/bugtrace/bugs/edit?id={bugId}`\n\nOr, even simpler - some TAPD instances have direct API endpoints for deletion. Let me check if there's a simple POST request I can make.\n\nActually, looking at the previous page data, I know the API endpoints. But for deletion specifically, TAPD typically uses POST requests. Let me try a different approach:\n\n1. Open the bug detail page\n2. Inspect for delete functionality\n3. Execute delete\n\nThe script I wrote has a 60s wait, which is too long. Let me just run it with a shorter wait or remove the wait entirely and just inspect.\n\nActually, let me take a simpler approach. Let me just run a quick headless inspection script first.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_iMXBtQ3MFprnjv9xDecU9265","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\inspect_delete.mjs","content":"import { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\nconst BUG_ID = '1131253609001016524';\nconst cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync('tapd_cookies.json','utf8'));\n\nconst browser = await chromium.launch({headless:true,args:['--no-sandbox','--disable-blink-features=AutomationControlled']});\nconst ctx = await browser.newContext({locale:'zh-CN',viewport:{width:1920,height:1080},userAgent:'Mozilla/5.0...Chrome/125.0.0.0 Safari/537.36'});\nawait ctx.addCookies(cookies);\nconst page = await ctx.newPage();\nawait page.addInitScript(()=>{delete navigator.webdriver;Object.defineProperty(navigator,'webdriver',{get:()=>false})});\n\nconst detailUrl = `https://www.tapd.cn/tapd_fe/31253609/bug/detail/${BUG_ID}`;\nawait page.goto(detailUrl, {waitUntil:'domcontentloaded',timeout:30000}).catch(e=>{});\nawait page.waitForTimeout(5000);\n\nconst info = await page.evaluate(() => {\n  const results = [];\n  // Find all buttons/links containing 删/更多/操作\n  document.querySelectorAll('a,button,span,[class*=more],[class*=action],[class*=operate]').forEach(el => {\n    const t = el.textContent?.trim();\n    if (!t) return;\n    if (t.includes('删')||t.includes('更多')||t.includes('操作')||t.includes('编辑')||t.includes('删除')) {\n      results.push({\n        text: t.substring(0,30),\n        id: el.id,\n        tag: el.tagName,\n        cls: el.className?.substring(0,80),\n        visible: el.offsetParent!==null,\n        href: el.href||'',\n        html: el.outerHTML?.substring(0,200)\n      });\n    }\n  });\n  return results;\n});\nconsole.log(JSON.stringify(info,null,2));\nawait browser.close();\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":57,"output":794,"cacheRead":58240,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":59091,"cost":{"input":0.00000798,"output":0.00022232000000000003,"cacheRead":0.00163072,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0018610200000000001}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778902863368,"responseId":"352a56f3-1607-498a-9128-996517a72575"}}
