{"type":"message","id":"62da6708","parentId":"c10f3f0a","timestamp":"2026-05-16T03:41:30.350Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I can see there's a \"删除\" (Delete) option in the page, but it's not visible (visible: false). It's inside a popover/dropdown menu. Looking at the structure:\n\n1. There's a \"更多\" (More) dropdown button on the page\n2. The \"更多\" dropdown has items: \"转需求\", \"复制缺陷\", \"移动缺陷\", \"合并缺陷\", \"关联重复缺陷\"\n3. There's also a \"删除\" (Delete) option, but it's not immediately visible without clicking \"更多\"\n\nWait, looking more carefully:\n- \"转需求  复制缺陷  移动缺陷  合并缺陷  关联重复缺陷 \" - visible, this is a header-more-operation menu\n- \"删除\" - visible: false, inside agi-dropdown-menu-item__text\n\nSo the delete option exists but might be in a different menu. Let me look for it.\n\nActually, I see there are TWO \"更多\" buttons:\n1. One in the header (fe-dropdown-nav-more brick) - this has \"转需求  复制缺陷  移动缺陷  合并缺陷  关联重复缺陷\" options\n2. One below in the more-item-wrap agi-dropdown - this is a tab-level \"更多\"\n\nThe \"删除\" option with visible:false is inside a popover that hasn't been triggered yet. Let me try clicking the \"更多\" button to see what options appear.\n\nActually, let me take a different approach. Instead of trying to find the delete button through the UI, let me try the TAPD API directly. TAPD uses AJAX calls. The delete action is probably a POST to some API endpoint.\n\nOr, I can use Playwright to:\n1. Click the \"更多\" button in the header\n2. Wait for the dropdown to appear\n3. Look for \"删除\" option and click it\n4. Confirm the delete dialog\n\nLet me write a proper script that does this.\n\nActually, the script needs to run headed because of WAF issues, but the user is watching. Let me write a clean script and run it.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"找到了，有个「更多」菜单，\"删除\"在里面。让我写个脚本点掉它。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_M0S0eZTJ3jSU3FmabG9H6071","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\delete_bug_final.mjs","content":"import { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\nimport path from 'path';\n\nconst BUG_ID = '1131253609001016524'; // First bug (with old screenshots)\nconst COOKIES_FILE = path.resolve('tapd_cookies.json');\n\n(async () => {\n  const cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(COOKIES_FILE, 'utf8'));\n\n  let headless = true;\n  let browser = await chromium.launch({\n    headless,\n    args: ['--no-sandbox', '--disable-blink-features=AutomationControlled']\n  });\n  let ctx = await browser.newContext({\n    locale: 'zh-CN',\n    viewport: { width: 1920, height: 1080 },\n    userAgent: 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 Chrome/125.0.0.0 Safari/537.36',\n  });\n  await ctx.addCookies(cookies);\n  let page = await ctx.newPage();\n  await page.addInitScript(() => { delete navigator.webdriver; Object.defineProperty(navigator,'webdriver',{get:()=>false}); });\n\n  try {\n    const detailUrl = `https://www.tapd.cn/tapd_fe/31253609/bug/detail/${BUG_ID}`;\n    await page.goto(detailUrl, { waitUntil: 'domcontentloaded', timeout: 30000 }).catch(e => {});\n    await page.waitForTimeout(5000);\n\n    if ((await page.title()).includes('WAF')) {\n      if (!headless) throw new Error('WAF blocked headed');\n      console.log('WAF blocked headless, retrying headed...');\n      await browser.close();\n      headless = false;\n      browser = await chromium.launch({ headless: false, args: ['--no-sandbox','--disable-blink-features=AutomationControlled'] });\n      ctx = await browser.newContext({ locale:'zh-CN', viewport:{width:1920,height:1080}, userAgent:'Mozilla/5.0...Chrome/125.0.0.0 Safari/537.36' });\n      await ctx.addCookies(cookies);\n      page = await ctx.newPage();\n      await page.addInitScript(() => { delete navigator.webdriver; Object.defineProperty(navigator,'webdriver',{get:()=>false}); });\n      await page.goto(detailUrl, { waitUntil:'domcontentloaded', timeout:30000 }).catch(e=>{});\n      await page.waitForTimeout(5000);\n    }\n\n    // Click \"更多\" to open the dropdown\n    const moreBtn = page.locator('.fe-dropdown-nav-more.brick a.dropdown-toggle').first();\n    if (await moreBtn.isVisible().catch(() => false)) {\n      await moreBtn.click();\n      await page.waitForTimeout(1500);\n      console.log('Clicked \"更多\"');\n    }\n\n    // Look for \"删除\" in the popover\n    const deleteBtn = page.locator('.agi-dropdown-menu-item__text:text(\"删除\"), .el-popover:visible span:text(\"删除\"), [class*=menu-item]:text(\"删除\")').first();\n    const delVisible = await deleteBtn.isVisible().catch(() => false);\n    if (delVisible) {\n      await deleteBtn.click();\n      await page.waitForTimeout(2000);\n      console.log('Clicked \"删除\"');\n\n      // Handle confirmation dialog\n      const confirmBtn = page.locator('.el-message-box:visible .el-button--primary, .dialog-footer .btn-primary, .ui-dialog:visible .btn-primary, .confirm:visible button:has-text(\"确定\"), button:has-text(\"确认删除\")').first();\n      if (await confirmBtn.isVisible().catch(() => false)) {\n        await confirmBtn.click();\n        await page.waitForTimeout(3000);\n        console.log('Confirmed deletion');\n      } else {\n        // Try generic confirm\n        await page.keyboard.press('Enter');\n        await page.waitForTimeout(3000);\n        console.log('Pressed Enter to confirm');\n      }\n\n      console.log('\\n✅ Bug deleted!');\n    } else {\n      // Debug: print what's visible in the popover\n      const popoverHtml = await page.evaluate(() => {\n        const pop = document.querySelector('.el-popover:not([aria-hidden=\"true\"])');\n        if (pop) return pop.textContent?.trim().substring(0,500);\n        const menus = document.querySelectorAll('[class*=menu]');\n        return Array.from(menus).slice(0,5).map(m => m.textContent?.trim().substring(0,200)).filter(Boolean);\n      });\n      console.log('Popover content:', popoverHtml);\n      await page.screenshot({ path: 'delete_popover.png' });\n    }\n\n    await page.waitForTimeout(2000);\n\n  } catch (e) {\n    console.error('Failed:', e.message);\n    await page.screenshot({ path: 'delete_error.png' }).catch(() => {});\n  } finally {\n    await browser.close();\n  }\n})();\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":2839,"output":1648,"cacheRead":59136,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63623,"cost":{"input":0.00039746000000000003,"output":0.00046144000000000003,"cacheRead":0.001655808,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002514708}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778902878943,"responseId":"c0d48f14-aa2b-4e8a-ad2b-84a1631a6d25"}}
