{"type":"message","id":"bdb0753a","parentId":"553256c1","timestamp":"2026-05-16T03:41:51.164Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK, clicking \"更多\" didn't show the delete option. The \"更多\" I clicked was a navigation dropdown, not the bug operation menu. Looking at the earlier inspection output more carefully:\n\nThere seem to be TWO \"更多\" buttons:\n1. `.fe-dropdown-nav-more.brick` - This is the **navigation** \"更多\" (shows more nav items) - this is the one I clicked\n2. `.more-item-wrap.agi-dropdown` with `.container-item-link.more-item-trigger` - This is the bug-level \"更多\" (shows operations like 删除)\n\nI need to click the second one, which is on the bug detail tab level, not the header navigation level.\n\nLet me look at the HTML structure more carefully:\n\nFor the second \"更多\" (tab-level):\n```html\n<div data-v-7b9fe202=\"\" class=\"more-item-wrap agi-dropdown\">\n  <span class=\"agi-popover__reference\">\n    <div role=\"tooltip\" id=\"el-popover-6015\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"el-popover el-popper agi-popover agi-popover--info agi-popover--custom agi-dropdown__popover \" t\n  ...\n  <span class=\"el-popover__reference-wrapper\">\n    <a data-v-7b9fe202=\"\" class=\"container-item-link more-item-trigger el-popover__reference\" ...>\n      <span data-v-7b9fe202=\"\" class=\"tab-name\">更多</span>\n    </a>\n  </span>\n</div>\n```\n\nSo the selector should be `.container-item-link.more-item-trigger` or `.more-item-wrap .tab-name:text(\"更多\")`.\n\nFor the delete button, looking at the menu items from the header \"更多\" (the first one I clicked) - those had \"转需求\", \"复制缺陷\", \"移动缺陷\", \"合并缺陷\", \"关联重复缺陷\". But that was the wrong menu.\n\nLet me look at the actual delete button more carefully. The \"删除\" was inside `.agi-dropdown-menu-item__text` with `visible: false`. This suggests it's in a different menu/dropdown.\n\nActually wait, I see the delete button was found on the page but wasn't visible. It might be in a context menu or in a different dropdown. Let me try clicking on the tab-level \"更多\" button and see what appears.\n\nLet me update the script to target the correct \"更多\" button.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"点错了\"更多\"，点到了导航栏那个。得点 Bug 详情页的操作\"更多\"。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_tBsnB3xQmqFZ1yn8kn6f6403","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\delete_bug_final.mjs","edits":[{"oldText":"    // Click \"更多\" to open the dropdown\n    const moreBtn = page.locator('.fe-dropdown-nav-more.brick a.dropdown-toggle').first();\n    if (await moreBtn.isVisible().catch(() => false)) {\n      await moreBtn.click();\n      await page.waitForTimeout(1500);\n      console.log('Clicked \"更多\"');\n    }","newText":"    // Click the bug-level \"更多\" (not the nav-level one)\n    const moreBtn = page.locator('.more-item-wrap .container-item-link.more-item-trigger').first();\n    if (await moreBtn.isVisible().catch(() => false)) {\n      await moreBtn.click();\n      await page.waitForTimeout(1500);\n      console.log('Clicked bug-level \"更多\"');\n    } else {\n      // Fallback: try broader selectors\n      const fallbackBtn = page.locator('a.container-item-link:has(span:text(\"更多\"))').first();\n      if (await fallbackBtn.isVisible().catch(() => false)) {\n        await fallbackBtn.click();\n        await page.waitForTimeout(1500);\n        console.log('Clicked fallback \"更多\"');\n      }\n    }"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":193,"output":917,"cacheRead":63872,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":64982,"cost":{"input":0.000027020000000000002,"output":0.00025676000000000003,"cacheRead":0.001788416,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002072196}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778902903897,"responseId":"dda9264f-9c76-4fb3-b27d-265058e7e42c"}}
