{"type":"message","id":"59cdc2b0","parentId":"603e776b","timestamp":"2026-05-16T03:43:08.073Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is taking too long. The \"更多\" buttons in the page are navigation elements, not bug operation menus. The visible \"删除\" text found was in the page root, not in a menu.\n\nThe problem is that the delete functionality in TAPD's new UI is in a different location. Looking at the original inspection, the \"删除\" was found in `.agi-dropdown-menu-item__text` with visible: false - this suggests it's in a dropdown that needs to be triggered by a specific action.\n\nLet me try a different approach. Instead of the detail page, let me try the **bug list page** where I can select the bug checkbox and use a batch operation. Or I could try the **edit page** URL format.\n\nActually, let me just check the edit page: `https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/bugtrace/bugs/edit?id=1131253609001016524`\n\nOn the edit page, there's often a visible \"删除\" button/option alongside save/cancel.\n\nLet me try a quick check of the edit page.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_7zpTEpp4ZxEWirAbj6k75257","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Set-Location C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace; node -e \"\nimport { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\nconst cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync('tapd_cookies.json','utf8'));\nconst browser = await chromium.launch({headless:true,args:['--no-sandbox','--disable-blink-features=AutomationControlled']});\nconst ctx = await browser.newContext({locale:'zh-CN',viewport:{width:1920,height:1080},userAgent:'Mozilla/5.0...Chrome/125.0.0.0'});\nawait ctx.addCookies(cookies);\nconst page = await ctx.newPage();\nawait page.addInitScript(()=>{delete navigator.webdriver;});\nawait page.goto('https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/bugtrace/bugs/edit?id=1131253609001016524',{waitUntil:'domcontentloaded',timeout:30000}).catch(e=>{});\nawait page.waitForTimeout(5000);\nconst dels = await page.evaluate(() => {\n  const d = document.querySelectorAll('[class*=\\\"del\\\" i], [class*=\\\"delete\\\" i], a:has(span:text(\\\"删\\\")), button:has(span:text(\\\"删\\\")), span:text(\\\"删\\\"), a:text(\\\"删\\\")');\n  return Array.from(d).filter(el => el.offsetParent!==null).slice(0,5).map(e=>({tag:e.tagName,text:e.textContent?.trim().substring(0,30),id:e.id,cls:e.className?.substring(0,60)}));\n});\nconsole.log(JSON.stringify(dels,null,2));\nawait browser.close();\n\" 2>&1","timeout":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":915,"output":671,"cacheRead":67328,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68914,"cost":{"input":0.0001281,"output":0.00018788000000000002,"cacheRead":0.001885184,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0022011640000000002}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778902981777,"responseId":"f9ec51a8-0a7b-4f2e-a1fd-830e12ef243a"}}
