{"type":"message","id":"c6c50fb5","parentId":"3fbf33d7","timestamp":"2026-05-16T03:44:18.493Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK so the edit page has a delete button (`<button class=\"btn btn-danger btn-ok\">删除</button>`) but it's not visible - it's likely in a confirmation dialog that hasn't been shown yet or is hidden behind some other interaction.\n\nAnd there's a \"更多\" button with class \"dropdown-toggle\" in the edit page. Let me try clicking that \"更多\" (which might be the bug operation menu on the edit page) to reveal the delete option.\n\nActually, looking at TAPD's edit page more carefully, there should be a \"更多操作\" (More Operations) dropdown in the header area. Clicking that should reveal options like \"删除\" (Delete), \"移动\" (Move), etc.\n\nLet me simplify - click that \"更多\" with class \"dropdown-toggle\" (the first one in the mores list that's an `<a>` tag) and see what happens. That should be the operation menu.\n\nLet me write a more focused script for this.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"找到删除按钮了，它在编辑页但被隐藏了。需要先点\"更多\"展开菜单。让我直接写个精简的脚本。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_TM6aMQPGdg4yQWySbzWB1720","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\do_delete.mjs","content":"import { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\nconst cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync('tapd_cookies.json','utf8'));\n\nlet browser = await chromium.launch({headless:false,args:['--no-sandbox','--disable-blink-features=AutomationControlled']});\nlet ctx = await browser.newContext({locale:'zh-CN',viewport:{width:1920,height:1080},userAgent:'Mozilla/5.0...Chrome/125.0.0.0'});\nawait ctx.addCookies(cookies);\nlet page = await ctx.newPage();\nawait page.addInitScript(()=>{delete navigator.webdriver;Object.defineProperty(navigator,'webdriver',{get:()=>false})});\n\ntry {\n  await page.goto('https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/bugtrace/bugs/edit?id=1131253609001016524',{waitUntil:'domcontentloaded',timeout:30000}).catch(e=>{});\n  await page.waitForTimeout(5000);\n\n  // Click \"更多\" dropdown in edit page header\n  const moreBtn = page.locator('.edit-header .dropdown-toggle, .btn-group .dropdown-toggle, a.dropdown-toggle:text(\"更多\")').first();\n  if (await moreBtn.isVisible().catch(()=>false)) {\n    await moreBtn.click();\n    await page.waitForTimeout(1500);\n    console.log('Clicked more dropdown');\n\n    // Now \"删除\" should be visible in the dropdown\n    const delBtn = page.locator('.dropdown-menu a:text(\"删除\"), .dropdown-menu button:text(\"删除\"), .dropdown-menu li:text(\"删除\")').first();\n    if (await delBtn.isVisible().catch(()=>false)) {\n      await delBtn.click();\n      await page.waitForTimeout(2000);\n      console.log('Clicked delete');\n\n      // Confirm dialog\n      const confirmBtn = page.locator('.ui-dialog .btn-primary, .el-dialog .el-button--primary, .modal .btn-primary, .confirm button:text(\"确定\"), button:text(\"确认删除\")').first();\n      if (await confirmBtn.isVisible().catch(()=>false)) {\n        await confirmBtn.click();\n        await page.waitForTimeout(3000);\n        console.log('\\n✅ Confirm delete ✓');\n      } else {\n        await page.keyboard.press('Enter');\n        await page.waitForTimeout(3000);\n        console.log('\\n✅ Pressed Enter to confirm');\n      }\n    }\n  } else {\n    // Try other approaches on the edit page\n    console.log('No more dropdown found, trying buttons...');\n    await page.screenshot({path:'edit_page.png'});\n    // List all visible buttons\n    const btns = await page.evaluate(() => {\n      return Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('a, button'))\n        .filter(e => e.offsetParent !== null)\n        .slice(0,20)\n        .map(e => ({tag:e.tagName, text:(e.textContent||'').trim().substring(0,30), id:e.id, cls:String(e.className||'').substring(0,50)}));\n    });\n    console.log(JSON.stringify(btns,null,2));\n  }\n} catch(e) {\n  console.error('Error:', e.message);\n} finally {\n  await browser.close();\n}\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":955,"output":1027,"cacheRead":71808,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":73790,"cost":{"input":0.0001337,"output":0.00028756,"cacheRead":0.002010624,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002431884}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778903050271,"responseId":"24e564b1-0d9e-4bb8-82c4-8cb16e936c8a"}}
