{"type":"message","id":"e54a36d8","parentId":"357bed23","timestamp":"2026-05-16T03:45:06.924Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The screenshot exists but I can't view it with the image model. Let me try a different approach. Let me just look at the edit page structure more carefully. The TAPD edit page typically has buttons at the top like \"保存\", \"取消\", and \"更多操作\".\n\nActually, from the earlier evaluation on the edit page, I found that there IS a delete button:\n```\n<button class=\"btn btn-danger btn-ok\">删除</button>\n```\nbut it was not visible. This is likely inside a confirmation dialog that's hidden.\n\nLet me think about this differently. On the TAPD edit page for bugs:\n1. There's probably a \"更多\" dropdown in the header\n2. Clicking it reveals \"删除\" option in the dropdown\n3. Clicking \"删除\" shows a confirmation dialog with the `btn btn-danger btn-ok` button\n\nThe issue is that clicking \"更多\" #0 didn't reveal \"删除\". This means either:\na. I clicked the wrong \"更多\" \nb. The dropdown menu appeared but the \"删除\" option isn't visible yet\n\nLet me click \"更多\" #4 instead, or try a different approach.\n\nActually, looking back at the original detail page inspection, the \"删除\" was found inside `.agi-dropdown-menu-item__text`. This is a Vue component (agi-dropdown). So the delete menu appears in a Vue-powered dropdown menu that only shows when the correct button is clicked.\n\nLet me try clicking \"更多\" #4 since it's also labeled \"更多\" and could be the right one.\n\nBut wait, maybe I should just write a simpler script that inspects the page more thoroughly - checking what menus/popovers become visible after each \"更多\" click.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_NjA0CYKh36BRwIUVqHU59972","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\delete_v4.mjs","content":"import { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\nconst cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync('tapd_cookies.json','utf8'));\n\nlet browser = await chromium.launch({headless:true,args:['--no-sandbox','--disable-blink-features=AutomationControlled']});\nlet ctx = await browser.newContext({locale:'zh-CN',viewport:{width:1920,height:1080},userAgent:'Mozilla/5.0...Chrome/125.0.0.0'});\nawait ctx.addCookies(cookies);\nlet page = await ctx.newPage();\nawait page.addInitScript(()=>{delete navigator.webdriver;Object.defineProperty(navigator,'webdriver',{get:()=>false})});\n\nasync function getVisiblePopupMenus() {\n  return await page.evaluate(() => {\n    const visibles = document.querySelectorAll('[class*=\"popover\"],[class*=\"menu\"],[class*=\"dropdown\"]');\n    return Array.from(visibles)\n      .filter(el => el.offsetParent !== null)\n      .slice(0,15)\n      .map(el => ({tag:el.tagName,text:(el.textContent||'').trim().substring(0,200),id:el.id,cls:String(el.className||'').substring(0,60)}));\n  });\n}\n\nawait page.goto('https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/bugtrace/bugs/edit?id=1131253609001016524',{waitUntil:'domcontentloaded',timeout:30000}).catch(e=>{});\nawait page.waitForTimeout(5000);\n\n// List all visible <a> tags with their text\nconst links = await page.evaluate(() => {\n  return Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('a'))\n    .filter(e => e.offsetParent !== null)\n    .slice(0,30)\n    .map(e => ({tag:e.tagName,text:(e.textContent||'').trim().substring(0,30),id:e.id,cls:String(e.className||'').substring(0,60),href:e.href?.substring(0,80)||''}));\n});\nconsole.log('All visible links:');\nlinks.forEach((l,i) => console.log(`${i}: \"${l.text}\" cls=\"${l.cls}\" href=\"${l.href}\"`));\n\n// Try clicking \"更多\" at index 4\nconst allMoreLinks = links.filter(l => l.text === '更多');\nconsole.log(`\\n\"更多\" links: ${allMoreLinks.length}`);\n\n// Click each \"更多\" by index\nfor (let mi = 0; mi < allMoreLinks.length; mi++) {\n  await page.goto('https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/bugtrace/bugs/edit?id=1131253609001016524',{waitUntil:'domcontentloaded',timeout:15000}).catch(e=>{});\n  await page.waitForTimeout(3000);\n  \n  // Get the actual nth \"更多\" link\n  const moreLinks = page.locator('a', { hasText: '更多' });\n  await moreLinks.nth(mi).click();\n  await page.waitForTimeout(2000);\n  \n  console.log(`\\n--- After clicking \"更多\" #${mi} ---`);\n  const menus = await getVisiblePopupMenus();\n  console.log('Visible popovers/dropdowns:', JSON.stringify(menus,null,2));\n  \n  // Check if \"删除\" text is visible anywhere\n  const hasDel = await page.evaluate(() => {\n    const all = document.querySelectorAll('*');\n    for (const el of all) {\n      if (el.offsetParent !== null && (el.textContent||'').includes('删除')) {\n        return {tag:el.tagName,text:(el.textContent||'').trim().substring(0,50),cls:String(el.className||'').substring(0,60)};\n      }\n    }\n    return null;\n  });\n  if (hasDel) {\n    console.log('Found \"删除\":', JSON.stringify(hasDel));\n  }\n}\n\nawait page.waitForTimeout(2000);\nawait browser.close();\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":13,"output":1337,"cacheRead":76544,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":77894,"cost":{"input":0.0000018200000000000002,"output":0.00037436,"cacheRead":0.002143232,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002519412}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778903096670,"responseId":"15b5059c-1237-4e86-bcb6-d26ddcb5354f"}}
