{"type":"message","id":"2eee1a57","parentId":"c3e7ed1e","timestamp":"2026-05-16T03:45:28.109Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Actually, this is getting way too complex. I've spent a lot of time on this. Let me take a completely different approach:\n\n1. Perhaps the TAPD edit page has a simple \"删除\" button that I missed. From the original inspection, we found `<button class=\"btn btn-danger btn-ok\">删除</button>` on the edit page. This was \"not visible\" but maybe it needs to be revealed by clicking some other button first.\n\n2. Or, let me try the OLD TAPD UI approach - the URL for the old bug edit page has a different format.\n\n3. Or, I could try a simple API call to delete the bug.\n\nActually, the simplest approach would be to just send a POST request to the TAPD API with the correct parameters. But I don't know the exact API endpoint for deletion.\n\nLet me try yet another approach - what if I use `page.evaluate` to directly trigger the delete via the DOM/TAPD's JavaScript? \n\nOr even simpler - let me just check what happens when I click \"更多\" dropdown #4. In the earlier headless test, dropdown toggle #4 was also \"更多\". Let me just click that one specifically.\n\nWait, actually, let me re-read the output:\n```\n#0: \"更多\"  - this is probably the header navigation \"更多\"\n#1: \"月圆之夜缺陷面板\" - workspace selector\n#2: \"添加\" - add button\n#3: \"\" - empty\n#4: \"更多\" - this could be the bug operation \"更多\"\n```\n\nI tried #0 and it didn't work. Let me try #4.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_5ib6pTwIONTu20Jg8sbT1805","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\delete_try4.mjs","content":"import { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\nconst cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync('tapd_cookies.json','utf8'));\n\nlet browser = await chromium.launch({headless:true,args:['--no-sandbox','--disable-blink-features=AutomationControlled']});\nlet ctx = await browser.newContext({locale:'zh-CN',viewport:{width:1920,height:1080},userAgent:'Mozilla/5.0...Chrome/125.0.0.0'});\nawait ctx.addCookies(cookies);\nlet page = await ctx.newPage();\nawait page.addInitScript(()=>{delete navigator.webdriver;});\n\nawait page.goto('https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/bugtrace/bugs/edit?id=1131253609001016524',{waitUntil:'domcontentloaded',timeout:30000}).catch(e=>{});\nawait page.waitForTimeout(5000);\n\n// Get ALL \"更多\" text nodes by clicking their parent anchors\nconst allAnchors = page.locator('a');\nconst anchorCount = await allAnchors.count();\nlet testedIndex = -1;\n\nfor (let i = 0; i < anchorCount; i++) {\n  const text = (await allAnchors.nth(i).textContent().catch(()=>''))?.trim() || '';\n  if (text === '更多') {\n    testedIndex = i;\n    console.log(`Testing anchor #${i} \"更多\"`);\n    await allAnchors.nth(i).click();\n    await page.waitForTimeout(2000);\n    \n    const menus = await page.evaluate(() => {\n      return Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('[class*=\"popover\"],[class*=\"dropdown\"],[class*=\"menu\"]'))\n        .filter(el => el.offsetParent !== null)\n        .slice(0,5)\n        .map(el => ({text:el.textContent?.trim().substring(0,200), cls:String(el.className||'').substring(0,60)}));\n    });\n    console.log('Menus:', menus.length ? menus.map(m=>m.text?.substring(0,100)).join(' | ') : '(none)');\n    \n    // Check for \"删除\" text\n    const delVisible = await page.evaluate(() => document.body.innerText.includes('删除'));\n    const delInPopup = menus.some(m => m.text?.includes('删除'));\n    console.log(`\"删除\" in page: ${delVisible}, in popup: ${delInPopup}`);\n    \n    if (delInPopup) {\n      // Find and click the delete option\n      const del = page.locator('span:text(\"删除\"), a:text(\"删除\"), div:text(\"删除\")').first();\n      await del.click();\n      await page.waitForTimeout(2000);\n      \n      // Confirm dialog\n      const confirm = page.locator('button:text(\"确认\"), button:text(\"确定\"), .btn-primary, .btn-danger').first();\n      if (await confirm.isVisible().catch(()=>false)) {\n        await confirm.click();\n        await page.waitForTimeout(3000);\n      } else {\n        await page.keyboard.press('Enter');\n      }\n      console.log('✅ Deleted!');\n      break;\n    }\n    \n    // Reload for next attempt\n    await page.goto('https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/bugtrace/bugs/edit?id=1131253609001016524',{waitUntil:'domcontentloaded',timeout:15000}).catch(e=>{});\n    await page.waitForTimeout(3000);\n  }\n}\n\nif (testedIndex === -1) console.log('No \"更多\" anchor found');\n\nawait browser.close();\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":133,"output":1221,"cacheRead":79232,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80586,"cost":{"input":0.00001862,"output":0.00034188,"cacheRead":0.002218496,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002578996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778903118556,"responseId":"d3ce0449-a7bd-4400-b4e6-02c5a1b9b9ab"}}
