{"type":"message","id":"13cdaf55","parentId":"6de84792","timestamp":"2026-05-16T03:46:52.250Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Let me now respond to the user with a summary of what was updated.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"搞定，已更新完成 ✅\n\n**更新的内容：**\n\n📄 **SKILL.md** (`plugin-skills/tapd-bug-create/`)\n- 附件上传步骤说明（用 `#file_input` + `setInputFiles` 加图片）\n- 用户发截图时自动附到 Bug 单\n- 补充了必填字段表和处理人自动补全用法\n- 提交按钮明确用 `#_view` 而不是隐藏的 `#save_return`\n\n📄 **create_bug.mjs**（脚本本体）\n- 新增 `attachments` 参数，支持传入图片路径数组自动上传\n\n📄 **MEMORY.md**\n- 记录了提交按钮、文件上传、附件目录路径\n\n以后提 Bug 单只要有图片，我会自动附上截图当证据。还有什么要改的吗？😎"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":103,"output":194,"cacheRead":91008,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":91305,"cost":{"input":0.000014420000000000001,"output":0.00005432,"cacheRead":0.002548224,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002616964}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778903209377,"responseId":"74631f0f-61d9-4f1c-9e79-91f8fac9be12"}}
