{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6f4adcea60a0c3dbc8b549df137\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yousan(叶枝君)\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-05-16 11:48 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yousan(叶枝君) (ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"name\": \"Yousan(叶枝君)\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"da816a85","parentId":"5b61fd46","timestamp":"2026-05-16T03:48:54.583Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"91cf4aff","parentId":"da816a85","timestamp":"2026-05-16T03:49:03.761Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to create a Story (需求) on TAPD with:\n- Title: \"测试测试\"\n- Some reference to \"客户端\" (client-side)\n\nThe Story create URL is `/31253609/prong/stories/add`.\n\nLooking at the SKILL.md, it mentions creating a Story through a different flow. The Story page has different fields from the Bug page. Let me look at what I know:\n\nFrom bug-fields.md:\n- Story URL: `https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/prong/stories/add`\n- Fields: StoryName, StoryPriority, StoryModule, StoryVersion, etc.\n- Submit: dynamically create submit input since there's no visible button\n\nLet me write a quick script to create this Story. The processing person should be \"叶枝君\" since it's a \"客户端\" (client-side) requirement and 叶枝君 handles code/program tasks.\n\nLet me write this script efficiently.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好，开个需求单给客户端。让我看看 Story 创建页的结构。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_HZYVyfMvIPQMj8oPNHjU1123","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Set-Location C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace; node -e \"\nimport { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\nconst cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync('tapd_cookies.json','utf8'));\nconst browser = await chromium.launch({headless:true,args:['--no-sandbox','--disable-blink-features=AutomationControlled']});\nconst ctx = await browser.newContext({locale:'zh-CN',viewport:{width:1920,height:1080},userAgent:'Mozilla/5.0...Chrome/125.0.0.0'});\nawait ctx.addCookies(cookies);\nconst page = await ctx.newPage();\nawait page.addInitScript(()=>{delete navigator.webdriver;Object.defineProperty(navigator,'webdriver',{get:()=>false})});\nawait page.goto('https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/prong/stories/add',{waitUntil:'domcontentloaded',timeout:30000}).catch(e=>{});\nawait page.waitForTimeout(5000);\n\nconst info = await page.evaluate(() => {\n  // Required fields\n  const fields = {};\n  ['#StoryName','#StoryPriority','#StoryModule','#StoryVersion','#StoryOwner','#StoryOwnerValue','#StoryCc'].forEach(sel => {\n    const el = document.querySelector(sel);\n    if (el) fields[sel] = {tag:el.tagName,type:el.type,visible:el.offsetParent!==null,class:el.className?.substring(0,60)};\n  });\n  // Submit buttons\n  const submits = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('[id*=\\\"save\\\"],[id*=\\\"submit\\\"],[type=\\\"submit\\\"],a.btn-primary')).filter(e=>e.offsetParent!==null).slice(0,5).map(e=>({tag:e.tagName,id:e.id,type:e.type,text:(e.textContent||'').trim().substring(0,30),name:e.name}));\n  // File upload\n  const fileInput = document.querySelector('input[type=\\\"file\\\"]')?.outerHTML?.substring(0,200) || 'none';\n  return {fields, submits, fileInput};\n});\nconsole.log(JSON.stringify(info,null,2));\nawait browser.close();\n\" 2>&1","timeout":25}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":83578,"output":783,"cacheRead":8064,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":92425,"cost":{"input":0.01170092,"output":0.00021924000000000002,"cacheRead":0.000225792,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.012145952000000002}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778903334583,"responseId":"57263405-e7ba-4772-a0de-e2bf4c0293ac"}}
