{"type":"message","id":"eaf228be","parentId":"27b551a4","timestamp":"2026-05-16T03:49:13.074Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Wait, I keep creating temp files that I then have to clean up. The user wants efficiency. Let me just use my knowledge of the TAPD Story create page.\n\nFrom the bug-fields.md reference:\n- Story URL: `https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/prong/stories/add`\n- Fields: StoryName (title), StoryPriority, StoryModule, StoryVersion\n- Submit: dynamically create `data[save_return]` submit input and click it\n\nFrom the SKILL.md:\n```javascript\n// URL: https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/prong/stories/add\nawait page.fill('#StoryName', 'Story title');\nawait page.selectOption('#StoryPriority', 'P1');\n// Submit requires dynamically creating a submit input:\nawait page.evaluate(() => {\n  const form = document.querySelector('form');\n  const btn = document.createElement('input');\n  btn.type = 'submit';\n  btn.name = 'data[save_return]';\n  btn.value = '提交&返回';\n  form.appendChild(btn);\n  btn.click();\n});\n```\n\nSo I need to:\n1. Fill title: \"测试测试\"\n2. Set priority (default to P2)\n3. Set module (客户端 -> probably \"核心玩法\" or \"系统功能\"? Let me just set it)\n4. Set handler to 叶枝君 (since it's a \"客户端\" requirement)\n5. Submit\n\nLet me write a quick script to do this. But actually, let me first run the inspect to see the page structure.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_2X6BMsTwhGaQdXdsivL38873","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Set-Location C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace; node inspect_story.mjs 2>&1","timeout":25}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":46,"output":408,"cacheRead":93312,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":93766,"cost":{"input":0.00000644,"output":0.00011424,"cacheRead":0.002612736,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0027334160000000002}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778903348373,"responseId":"ad7e795e-260