{"type":"message","id":"77b08b3a","parentId":"9c42b36c","timestamp":"2026-05-16T04:02:01.205Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[message_id: om_x100b6f4a8d87e4a0c2e93d7a3c3fc75]\nYousan(叶枝君): 开单成功，但是忘记了我昨天给你的规则，开客户端单的时候，只需要客户端，qa和策划"}],"timestamp":1778904121203}}
