{"type":"message","id":"169b6156","parentId":"27c88a0e","timestamp":"2026-05-16T04:02:07.363Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying I forgot the rules about creating requirement/story tickets for \"客户端\" (client-side). Let me recall what was discussed yesterday about this.\n\nLooking at the information I have in MEMORY.md and daily notes... I don't see any specific rule about 客户端 requirement creation in my memory files. Let me search for it.\n\nThe user mentioned that for 客户端 (client) requirements, only three groups need to be involved: 客户端, QA, and 策划. This likely means:\n- Handler: 叶枝君 (客户端/程序)\n- CC/related: QA (测试) and 策划 (design)\n\nWait, the user said \"开客户端单的时候，只需要客户端，qa和策划\" - when creating a client-side requirement ticket, only need client (dev), QA, and design/planning.\n\nSo this is probably about the preset sub-work items or the items that get created alongside the story. In TAPD when creating a Story, there are \"PresetItems\" (预设子工作项) that can be checked. The rule is:\n- For 客户端 requirements, only check: 客户端, QA, 策划 options\n- Don't check other options like UI, 特效, etc.\n\nThis was a rule the user established yesterday that I forgot to implement. Let me search my memory for this.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"抱歉主人，昨天这话我确实没记下来。让我查一下。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_lhjj7Lds67pLFi9vE0Ua3275","name":"memory_search","arguments":{"query":"客户端 需求单 规则 预设子工作项","corpus":"memory"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":32439,"output":360,"cacheRead":65536,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":98335,"cost":{"input":0.004541460000000001,"output":0.00010080000000000001,"cacheRead":0.001835008,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0064772680000000004}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778904121206,"responseId":"0b03210b-59e9-4e4b-907f-dca3fd1bec83"}}
{"type":"message","id":"c095a185","parentId":"169b6156","timestamp":"2026-05-16T04:02:08.216Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_lhjj7Lds67pLFi9vE0Ua3275","toolName":"memory_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"5ffaf3b8c9e04e5cfa54178142540ab72bfd0795ae39dc0de56d6110c1f82c5d\",\n      \"path\": \"memory/2026-05-15.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 101,\n      \"endLine\": 129,\n      \"score\": 1,\n      \"textScore\": 0.585782512501375,\n      \"snippet\": \"- Cookie 已保存到 `workspace/tapd_cookies.json`\\n- Storage state 已保存到 `workspace/tapd_storage.json`\\n- 登录用户：枝君（workspace 31253609 可访问）\\n- 备用：邮箱/密码登录、手机号+验证码、微信扫码\\n\\n### TAPD API 关键发现\\n- 查询 Bug 列表：`POST /api/aggregation/bug_aggregation/get_bugs_list`\\n- 查询 Bug 详情：`POST /api/aggregation/workitem_aggregation/common_get_info`\\n- 创建 Bug 页面：`/31253609/bugtrace/bugs/add`\\n- 创建 Story 页面：`/31253609/prong/stories/add`\\n- 编辑 Bug 页面：`/31253609/bugtrace/bugs/edit?id={bugId}`\\n- CSRF token cookie：`dsc-token`\\n- 提交按钮：`#save_return`（提交&返回）、`#save_view`（提交&查看）\\n\\n### Bug 字段表\\n| 字段 | 表单 name | 规则 |\\n|------|-----------|------|\\n| 标题 | `data[Bug][title]` | #BugTitle，必填 |\\n| 发现版本 | `data[Bug][version_report]` | #BugVersionReport，必填\\n\\nSource: memory/2026-05-15.md#L101-L129\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/2026-05-15.md#L101-L129\",\n      \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"provider\": \"none\",\n  \"citations\": \"auto\",\n  \"debug\": {\n    \"backend\": \"builtin\",\n    \"effectiveMode\": \"n/a\",\n    \"searchMs\": 761,\n    \"hits\": 1\n  }\n}"}],"details":{"results":[{"id":"5ffaf3b8c9e04e5cfa54178142540ab72bfd0795ae39dc0de56d6110c1f82c5d","path":"memory/2026-05-15.md","startLine":101,"endLine":129,"score":1,"textScore":0.585782512501375,"snippet":"- Cookie 已保存到 `workspace/tapd_cookies.json`\n- Storage state 已保存到 `workspace/tapd_storage.json`\n- 登录用户：枝君（workspace 31253609 可访问）\n- 备用：邮箱/密码登录、手机号+验证码、微信扫码\n\n### TAPD API 关键发现\n- 查询 Bug 列表：`POST /api/aggregation/bug_aggregation/get_bugs_list`\n- 查询 Bug 详情：`POST /api/aggregation/workitem_aggregation/common_get_info`\n- 创建 Bug 页面：`/31253609/bugtrace/bugs/add`\n- 创建 Story 页面：`/31253609/prong/stories/add`\n- 编辑 Bug 页面：`/31253609/bugtrace/bugs/edit?id={bugId}`\n- CSRF token cookie：`dsc-token`\n- 提交按钮：`#save_return`（提交&返回）、`#save_view`（提交&查看）\n\n### Bug 字段表\n| 字段 | 表单 name | 规则 |\n|------|-----------|------|\n| 标题 | `data[Bug][title]` | #BugTitle，必填 |\n| 发现版本 | `data[Bug][version_report]` | #BugVersionReport，必填\n\nSource: memory/2026-05-15.md#L101-L129","source":"memory","citation":"memory/2026-05-15.md#L101-L129","corpus":"memory"}],"provider":"none","citations":"auto","debug":{"backend":"builtin","effectiveMode":"n/a","searchMs":761,"hits":1}},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778904128216}}
