{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6f4a8891f4a4c291c3560e16a91\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yousan(叶枝君)\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-05-16 12:02 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yousan(叶枝君) (ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"name\": \"Yousan(叶枝君)\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"8e865339","parentId":"a0eca36c","timestamp":"2026-05-16T04:02:49.985Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"cb13f2b2","parentId":"8e865339","timestamp":"2026-05-16T04:02:58.661Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user confirmed the rule:\n- 客户端需求单 → 只勾选：客户端、QA、策划\n- 不勾选：UI、特效等\n\nNow I need to:\n1. First, figure out what the preset items look like on the TAPD Story creation page\n2. Update the SKILL.md with this rule\n3. Update the create_story.mjs script to handle preset items\n\nLet me first inspect the Story page to find the preset items checkboxes. I need to understand how TAPD renders them.\n\nFor the existing \"测试测试\" test story, the user said \"好的\" which seems to confirm my suggestion to delete and recreate it properly. But actually they just said \"好的\" to my confirmation of the rule. Let me ask if they want me to fix the test story too, or proceed to update the skill.\n\nActually, let me just focus on:\n1. First, inspect the Story page to understand preset items structure\n2. Update SKILL.md with the rule\n3. Update the create_story script\n\nLet me start by inspecting the Story page for the preset items.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好，先看看需求页的预设子工作项长什么样，然后更新脚本。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_cAn61uv6pGU1i3y1WiZF8908","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\inspect_preset.mjs","content":"import { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\nconst cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync('tapd_cookies.json','utf8'));\nconst browser = await chromium.launch({headless:true,args:['--no-sandbox','--disable-blink-features=AutomationControlled']});\nconst ctx = await browser.newContext({locale:'zh-CN',viewport:{width:1920,height:1080},userAgent:'Mozilla/5.0...Chrome/125.0.0.0'});\nawait ctx.addCookies(cookies);\nconst page = await ctx.newPage();\nawait page.addInitScript(()=>{delete navigator.webdriver;Object.defineProperty(navigator,'webdriver',{get:()=>false})});\nawait page.goto('https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/prong/stories/add',{waitUntil:'domcontentloaded',timeout:30000}).catch(e=>{});\nawait page.waitForTimeout(5000);\n\n// Find all preset sub-work items (checkboxes)\nconst presetInfo = await page.evaluate(() => {\n  // Look for checkboxes and their labels\n  const checkboxes = document.querySelectorAll('input[type=\"checkbox\"]');\n  const results = [];\n  checkboxes.forEach(cb => {\n    // Find label by for attribute\n    let label = '';\n    if (cb.id) {\n      const lbl = document.querySelector('label[for=\"'+cb.id+'\"]');\n      if (lbl) label = lbl.textContent?.trim() || '';\n    }\n    // Also check parent text\n    if (!label) {\n      const parent = cb.closest('label') || cb.parentElement;\n      if (parent) label = parent.textContent?.trim() || '';\n    }\n    results.push({\n      id: cb.id,\n      name: cb.name,\n      value: cb.value || '',\n      checked: cb.checked,\n      visible: cb.offsetParent !== null,\n      label: label.substring(0,50),\n      html: cb.outerHTML?.substring(0,200)\n    });\n  });\n  return results;\n});\nconsole.log('=== All checkboxes ===');\npresetInfo.forEach((c,i) => console.log(`${i}: ${JSON.stringify(c)}`));\nconsole.log('\\n=== Checkbox count:', presetInfo.length);\n\n// Also look for the PresetItems naming pattern\nconst presetNames = presetInfo.filter(c => c.name && c.name.includes('PresetItems'));\nconsole.log('\\n=== PresetItems checkboxes only:');\npresetNames.forEach(c => console.log(JSON.stringify(c)));\n\nawait browser.close();\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":10240,"output":884,"cacheRead":91392,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":102516,"cost":{"input":0.0014336000000000002,"output":0.00024752000000000004,"cacheRead":0.002558976,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0042400960000000005}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778904169985,"responseId":"32584894-5625-47e3-ae6c-080764a51c11"}}
