{"type":"message","id":"a6f91659","parentId":"d1f94370","timestamp":"2026-05-16T04:03:25.640Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So the checkboxes are NOT named `PresetItems[N][create_task]` as I thought. They're checkboxes for `data[Story][custom_field_11]` which seems to be an asset type field (音效, 语音, 音乐, UI界面, 1V1). Not preset sub-work items.\n\nThe \"预设子工作项\" mentioned in bug-fields.md might be different from what I see here. Let me look more carefully at the page content to find the preset sub-work items section. The presets might be in a different section of the page, like a \"预设子工作项\" tab or section.\n\nLet me search for text that contains \"任务\" or \"预设\" in the page.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_LoqX9o1uc2WPjJ18HFXX8158","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\inspect_preset2.mjs","content":"import { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\nconst cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync('tapd_cookies.json','utf8'));\nconst browser = await chromium.launch({headless:true,args:['--no-sandbox','--disable-blink-features=AutomationControlled']});\nconst ctx = await browser.newContext({locale:'zh-CN',viewport:{width:1920,height:1080},userAgent:'Mozilla/5.0...Chrome/125.0.0.0'});\nawait ctx.addCookies(cookies);\nconst page = await ctx.newPage();\nawait page.addInitScript(()=>{delete navigator.webdriver;});\nawait page.goto('https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/prong/stories/add',{waitUntil:'domcontentloaded',timeout:30000}).catch(e=>{});\nawait page.waitForTimeout(5000);\n\nconst allText = await page.evaluate(() => document.body.innerText);\nconsole.log('Body text (first 3000 chars):');\nconsole.log(allText.substring(0,3000));\n\n// Also search for preset task HTML\nconst presetHTML = await page.evaluate(() => {\n  const results = [];\n  // Search for sections containing 预设 or 子工作 or task\n  document.querySelectorAll('.section, .field, fieldset, [class*=preset], [class*=task], [class*=workitem], [class*=child]').forEach(el => {\n    results.push({\n      class: (el.className||'').substring(0,80),\n      text: (el.textContent||'').trim().substring(0,200),\n      visible: el.offsetParent !== null\n    });\n  });\n  return results.slice(0,20);\n});\nconsole.log('\\n=== Preset/Task sections ===');\nconsole.log(JSON.stringify(presetHTML,null,2));\n\nawait browser.close();\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":629,"output":641,"cacheRead":102784,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":104054,"cost":{"input":0.00008806000000000001,"output":0.00017948,"cacheRead":0.002877952,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003145492}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778904199951,"responseId":"297a3e06-9cff-4412-8966-a36a5e833518"}}
