{"type":"message","id":"7f3efa66","parentId":"df05e08e","timestamp":"2026-05-16T04:03:32.344Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Wait, the user said \"只需要客户端，qa和策划\" - \"只需要\" means \"only need\". This could mean only need to assign/notify 客户端, QA and 策划.\n\nMaybe the rule isn't about preset sub-work items at all. Maybe it's about:\n1. The handler/CC fields - only add 客户端 person, QA person, and 策划 person\n2. Or the module field - only select certain modules\n3. Or the preset items\n\nBut actually, looking at what I know about TAPD requirement creation, for a \"客户端\" (client-side) requirement:\n- Handler: 叶枝君 (客户端 dev)\n- It needs to involve QA and 策划 too\n\nSo \"只需要客户端，qa和策划\" might mean:\n- The requirement is assigned to 客户端 (client dev)\n- With QA and 策划 as followers/participants\n\nSo it's about the CC or related fields, not preset sub-work items. Or it could mean the preset child work items that get created for the requirement should only include those three categories.\n\nWait, but I don't want to keep guessing. Let me first run the inspect_preset2 to get more info, and also think about what the user actually said.\n\nActually, re-reading the user's message: \"开客户端单的时候，只需要客户端，qa和策划\" — when creating client-side requirements, only [include/tick] client, QA and planning/design.\n\nGiven TAPD's Story creation page has:\n- 预设子工作项 (Preset sub-work items) - checkboxes for automatically creating child tasks\n- Or it could be about which people to add as handler/participants\n\nSince there are 17 presets mentioned in bug-fields.md, and the user says \"只需要\" (only need) three of them, this is likely about the preset sub-work items.\n\nBut the checkboxes I found were for `data[Story][custom_field_11]` (asset type), not PresetItems. The PresetItems might be in a different section of the page.\n\nLet me run the inspect script and see.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_kJM0xTeL4jik1s73wR8F3141","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Set-Location C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace; node inspect_preset2.mjs 2>&1","timeout":20}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":160,"output":526,"cacheRead":103936,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":104622,"cost":{"input":0.000022400000000000002,"output":0.00014728,"cacheRead":0.002910208,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0030798880000000002}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778904205659,"responseId":"77713748-fa22-46ca-836a-2d8e83869f70"}}
