{"type":"message","id":"f3265fab","parentId":"c3fff9bb","timestamp":"2026-05-16T04:03:46.143Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I can see \"预设子工作项 将同步创建 17 项 预设子工作项\" in the body text. So there ARE 17 preset items. But the workitem-icon__mini elements show categories like T, N, F, S, V, B, F, S, A, A, A, C, S, S, O, A, S.\n\nThe user wants to only check: 客户端, QA, 策划. Let me find these checkboxes in the page.\n\nFrom bug-fields.md:\n```\n### 预设子工作项\n\n创建需求时，可通过 `data[PresetItems][N][create_task]` 勾选预设的子工作项（共17个预设，如 T 任务、N 月圆新手、F 月圆战斗、S 战斗子任务等）。\n```\n\nThe workitem type icons are:\nT = T 任务 (generic task)\nN = N 月圆新手 (NFM New Player)\nF = F 月圆战斗 (NFM Combat)\nS = S 战斗子任务 (Combat Sub-task)\nV = ?\nB = ?\nA = ?\nC = ?\nO = ?\n\nHmm, the user said 客户端, QA, 策划. These names don't quite match the letter icons. Let me find the actual checkbox names.\n\nLet me look for the preset items HTML structure more carefully. The \"预设子工作项\" section likely contains checkboxes or toggle switches hidden behind some click action.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_57jCQp09SuL8Y8W5sayM0136","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Set-Location C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace; node -e \"\nimport { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\nconst cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync('tapd_cookies.json','utf8'));\nconst browser = await chromium.launch({headless:true,args:['--no-sandbox','--disable-blink-features=AutomationControlled']});\nconst ctx = await browser.newContext({locale:'zh-CN',viewport:{width:1920,height:1080},userAgent:'Mozilla/5.0...Chrome/125.0.0.0'});\nawait ctx.addCookies(cookies);\nconst page = await ctx.newPage();\nawait page.addInitScript(()=>{delete navigator.webdriver;});\nawait page.goto('https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/prong/stories/add',{waitUntil:'domcontentloaded',timeout:30000}).catch(e=>{});\nawait page.waitForTimeout(5000);\n\n// Find the preset section HTML\nconst html = await page.evaluate(() => {\n  const results = [];\n  document.querySelectorAll('input[type=checkbox]').forEach(cb => {\n    const parent = cb.closest('li') || cb.closest('div') || cb.parentElement;\n    const label = parent?.textContent?.trim() || cb.id;\n    results.push({id:cb.id, name:cb.name, value:cb.value, checked:cb.checked, label:label.substring(0,80)});\n  });\n  return results;\n});\nconsole.log('Checkbox results:');\nhtml.forEach((c,i) => console.log(i + ': ' + JSON.stringify(c)));\n\" 2>&1","timeout":20}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1023,"output":740,"cacheRead":104576,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":106339,"cost":{"input":0.00014322,"output":0.00020720000000000002,"cacheRead":0.002928128,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003278548}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778904219581,"responseId":"49ef9d1b-c3f5-4104-9f6d-0b295e02bbf6"}}
