{"type":"message","id":"2576259f","parentId":"71ad4f43","timestamp":"2026-05-16T04:04:20.289Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"There are only 5 checkboxes on the page, all for `custom_field_11` (asset type). No PresetItems checkboxes. The preset items might be represented differently - perhaps through a separate UI component (like a toggle/tag system) rather than checkboxes.\n\nThe page text says \"预设子工作项 将同步创建 17 项 预设子工作项\" - so 17 items will be created by default. The checkboxes aren't the preset items.\n\nMaybe the preset items are created by default and there's a way to customize them. The TAPD Story creation page might have a separate configuration for presets that's controlled by the template, not by individual checkboxes on the create page.\n\nOr maybe the \"只需要客户端，qa和策划\" rule refers to something else entirely - like:\n- The **cc/抄送** field: only add 客户端(叶枝君), QA(test), and 策划\n- The **handler** should be just 叶枝君\n- No need to CC UI/特效 people\n\nActually, looking at the body text I found earlier, there were workitem icons like T, N, F, S, V, B, F, S, A, A, A, C, S, S, O, A, S (17 items). These might be preset tasks that are auto-created. Some of these likely correspond to:\n- 客户端 (Client) - could be T (Task) or something\n- QA - could be something\n- 策划 (Design) - could be something\n\nBut without seeing the UI, I can't tell exactly.\n\nActually, maybe the preset items are auto-created and can't be individually checked/unchecked from the UI. The rule \"只需要客户端，qa和策划\" might mean that those are the only preset sub-work items that should be created, and the rest should be deselected.\n\nOr, more likely, this is about the module/field assignment on the Story form itself:\n- Module: 客户端-related module\n- Handler: 叶枝君\n- Related: QA and 策划\n\nActually, you know what, let me just ask the user to clarify since I don't have this info. But the user seems to expect me to know this from yesterday.\n\nLet me look at it from a different angle - the checkboxes for custom_field_11 include: 音效, 语音, 音乐, UI界面, 1V1 - these are \"audio types\" (音频类型). The text says \"音频类型\" before these checkboxes. So these are not the preset sub-work items.\n\nThe preset sub-work items must be auto-generated from the template and not individually configurable per-story. The rule about \"只需要客户端，qa和策划\" is probably about something else.\n\nWait, I just re-read it: \"开客户端单的时候，只需要客户端，qa和策划\"\n\nMaybe this means: when creating a client-side requirement, the requirement only involves: client (dev), QA, and design teams. So the Story's related fields/handler should reflect that:\n- Handler: 叶枝君 (客户端)\n- CC should include QA and 策划 (赵乾)\n- NOT include UI, 特效, etc.\n\nBut currently my story creation script already sets handler to 叶枝君 and CC to 周以天. Maybe the CC should be different for client-side requirements.\n\nHmm, but the user just said \"好的\" to confirm. Let me not overthink this. Let me ask the user directly: \"客户端、QA、策划 在TAPD上对应的用户名/角色是什么？\"","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我检查了一下，需求页上没找到预设子工作项的勾选框，它们应该是自动根据模板生成的。\n\n你说的「只需要客户端、QA和策划」具体是指：\n\n1. **处理人/抄送人** — 只加叶枝君（客户端）、QA、赵乾（策划），不加UI/特效这些？\n2. 还是 **预设子工作项** 只创建这三类的？\n\n能告诉我对应的 TAPD 用户名吗？这样我直接写进脚本自动处理好 😎"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":328,"output":853,"cacheRead":106496,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":107677,"cost":{"input":0.00004592,"output":0.00023884,"cacheRead":0.002981888,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0032666479999999996}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778904250389,"responseId":"dafa8411-fb1e-42d5-8cb7-3d8b9990b878"}}
