{"type":"message","id":"2fc61892","parentId":"039bfbc4","timestamp":"2026-05-16T04:06:01.061Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK so the rule is about \"预设子工作项\" (preset sub-work items). When creating a client-side requirement, only 3 preset items should be checked: 客户端, QA, 策划.\n\nBut from my inspection, the preset items on the Story page don't have regular checkbox inputs. The checkboxes I found were for `custom_field_11` (asset type). The preset items are probably created via a different mechanism.\n\nThe body text mentioned workitem icons: T, N, F, S, V, B, F, S, A, A, A, C, S, S, O, A, S (17 presets).\n\nAnd in the bug-fields.md it says:\n```\n### 预设子工作项\n\n创建需求时，可通过 `data[PresetItems][N][create_task]` 勾选预设的子工作项（共17个预设，如 T 任务、N 月圆新手、F 月圆战斗、S 战斗子任务等）。\n```\n\nSo the inputs should be named like `data[PresetItems][0][create_task]` etc. But my inspect didn't find any such inputs. Maybe they're rendered differently or need to be clicked/expanded first.\n\nLet me look more carefully at the page. The \"预设子工作项\" section might be a collapsible section that needs to be expanded to see the checkboxes.\n\nLet me inspect the HTML more carefully around the \"预设子工作项\" text to find hidden/collapsible sections.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"明白了，是预设子工作项！让我找找它们的具体结构。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_QZumizurGJruPVIMVT2z8624","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\inspect_preset3.mjs","content":"import { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\nconst cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync('tapd_cookies.json','utf8'));\nconst browser = await chromium.launch({headless:true,args:['--no-sandbox','--disable-blink-features=AutomationControlled']});\nconst ctx = await browser.newContext({locale:'zh-CN',viewport:{width:1920,height:1080},userAgent:'Mozilla/5.0...Chrome/125.0.0.0'});\nawait ctx.addCookies(cookies);\nconst page = await ctx.newPage();\nawait page.addInitScript(()=>{delete navigator.webdriver;});\nawait page.goto('https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/prong/stories/add',{waitUntil:'domcontentloaded',timeout:30000}).catch(e=>{});\nawait page.waitForTimeout(5000);\n\n// Get the HTML near \"预设子工作项\"\nconst presetSection = await page.evaluate(() => {\n  const allHTML = document.body.innerHTML;\n  const idx = allHTML.indexOf('预设子工作项');\n  if (idx === -1) return 'Not found';\n  return allHTML.substring(Math.max(0, idx - 500), idx + 2000);\n});\nconsole.log('HTML around \"预设子工作项\":');\nconsole.log(presetSection);\nawait browser.close();\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":9420,"output":711,"cacheRead":98304,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":108435,"cost":{"input":0.0013188000000000002,"output":0.00019908000000000003,"cacheRead":0.002752512,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004270392}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778904354070,"responseId":"c36f7647-7d6a-4efb-92fe-1d978e30bcf8"}}
