ass=\"associated-object-more\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"dropdown more\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"preset-workitems-info\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t将同步创建 <span class=\"preset-workitems j-edit-preset-tasks__num\">17 项</span> 预设子工作项\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"edit-workitems-relation j-edit-preset-stories\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i class=\"font font-edit\"></i>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<input type=\"hidden\" class=\"j-auto-succeed-name__form\" name=\"data[auto_succeed_story_name]\" value=\"1\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<input type=\"hidden\" class=\"j-auto-succeed-fields__form\" name=\"data[auto_succeed_story_fields]\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"preset-story-names-icon\"></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"fe-vue-component\"><!----></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<script id=\"preset-dialog-story__template\" type=\"text/html\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"editform-name-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img height=\"11\" title=\"任务\" src=\"https://viper.tapd.cn/icon/files/31253609/icon/1131253609001000182.png?token=633ce574e14ca2a8a7cbd5e55718e57c219b79d83be3293d77c48247cbb17a12&version=1726303883&company_id=61182352\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"editform-name-row__story\" title=\"<%= name %>\"><%= name %></span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</script>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<script id=\"preset-dialog-task__template\" type=\"text/html\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"editform-table-ico\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img height=\"11\" class=\"story-image j-preset-story-workitem-type__img\" title=\"<%= relate_workitem_type_title %>\" style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align: -2px; height: 11px;margin-right: 2px;vertical-align: baseline;\" relate_workitem_type_id=\"<%= relate_workitem_type_id %>\" <%= relate_workitem_type_disabled_attr  %> src=\"<%= relate_workitem_type_src %>\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"editform-table-prefix\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"editform-name-row__prefix\" title=\"<%= prefix %>\"><%= prefix %></span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"editform-table-spliter\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"editform-name-row__spliter\"> - </span>","cwd":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778904370122}}
{"type":"message","id":"a453f329","parentId":"463880cb","timestamp":"2026-05-16T04:06:18.447Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the HTML! The preset items section shows:\n1. \"预设子工作项\" text\n2. \"将同步创建 17 项 预设子工作项\" count\n3. An edit button: `<span class=\"edit-workitems-relation j-edit-preset-stories\"><i class=\"font font-edit\"></i></span>`\n4. Hidden inputs: `j-auto-succeed-name__form` and `j-auto-succeed-fields__form`\n5. The preset items are rendered using a dialog/script template (`preset-dialog-story__template` and `preset-dialog-task__template`)\n\nAnd I can see the toggle icons (preset task type icons). The section has a `<span class=\"edit-workitems-relation j-edit-preset-stories\">` with an edit icon that probably opens a dialog to customize which presets are included.\n\nSo the flow would be:\n1. Click the edit icon (`.j-edit-preset-stories`)\n2. This opens a dialog showing all 17 preset work items\n3. Each has a checkbox\n4. Uncheck the ones we don't want, keep only 客户端, QA, 策划\n5. Save/confirm the dialog\n\nThe interesting thing is the hidden inputs:\n- `data[auto_succeed_story_name]` - whether to auto-generate story names\n- `data[auto_succeed_story_fields]` - comma-separated fields to auto-succeed\n\nAnd there's `data[PresetItems][N][create_task]` from the bug-fields.md - these checkboxes are probably in the dialog that pops up when clicking the edit icon.\n\nLet me write a script to:\n1. Click the edit icon to open the preset dialog\n2. Read the dialog contents to see the preset items and their names\n3. Figure out which ones correspond to 客户端, QA, 策划\n\nLet me update the inspection script.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"找到了！预设子工作项有个编辑按钮（铅笔图标）点击后会弹窗显示17个选项。让我看看弹窗内容。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_hOLYHYk25u0iouZuLS8x9180","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\inspect_dialog.mjs","content":"import { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\nconst cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync('tapd_cookies.json','utf8'));\nconst browser = await chromium.launch({headless:true,args:['--no-sandbox','--disable-blink-features=AutomationControlled']});\nconst ctx = await browser.newContext({locale:'zh-CN',viewport:{width:1920,height:1080},userAgent:'Mozilla/5.0...Chrome/125.0.0.0'});\nawait ctx.addCookies(cookies);\nconst page = await ctx.newPage();\nawait page.addInitScript(()=>{delete navigator.webdriver;});\nawait page.goto('https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/prong/stories/add',{waitUntil:'domcontentloaded',timeout:30000}).catch(e=>{});\nawait page.waitForTimeout(5000);\n\n// Click the edit icon to open preset dialog\nconst editBtn = page.locator('.j-edit-preset-stories').first();\nawait editBtn.click();\nawait page.waitForTimeout(2000);\n\n// Now read the dialog content\nconst dialogHTML = await page.evaluate(() => {\n  // Find the dialog\n  const dialog = document.querySelector('.ui-dialog, [class*=dialog], [class*=modal], .el-dialog');\n  if (dialog) {\n    return dialog.outerHTML?.substring(0,5000);\n  }\n  // Try finding the dialog by looking at what became visible\n  const allVis = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('*')).filter(e => {\n    const t = e.textContent?.trim() || '';\n    return e.offsetParent !== null && (t.includes('预设') || t.includes('子工作') || t.includes('任务'));\n  });\n  return allVis.slice(0,10).map(e => ({\n    tag: e.tagName,\n    text: e.textContent?.trim().substring(0,200),\n    id: e.id,\n    cls: (e.className||'').substring(0,80)\n  }));\n});\nconsole.log('Dialog content:', typeof dialogHTML === 'string' ? dialogHTML.substring(0,3000) : JSON.stringify(dialogHTML, null, 2));\n\n// Take a screenshot for review\nawait page.screenshot({path:'preset_dialog.png'});\nconsole.log('\\nScreenshot saved to preset_dialog.png');\n\nawait browser.close();\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":787,"output":1037,"cacheRead":108544,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":110368,"cost":{"input":0.00011018,"output":0.00029036000000000003,"cacheRead":0.003039232,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003439772}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778904370124,"responseId":"400d6036-d3b0-4535-a986-8b55fdac06e7"}}
