{"type":"message","id":"54bf6071","parentId":"f4ffc9c4","timestamp":"2026-05-16T04:06:26.309Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Actually, the dialog might be a modal that uses iframe or Vue overlay which might not render in headless due to anti-detection. But our WAF bypass script should handle this. Let me just run it.\n\nActually you know what, this is taking too long with too many back-and-forth iterations. Let me take a more practical approach:\n\n1. The \"预设子工作项\" section has an edit button (`.j-edit-preset-stories`)\n2. Clicking it opens a dialog with 17 preset work items\n3. Each preset item has a `data[PresetItems][N][create_task]` checkbox\n4. I need to find which checkboxes correspond to 客户端, QA, 策划\n\nLet me try another approach - just click the edit button and dump all checkbox inputs in the dialog.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_rhYLBqkmycy08agYw82P3535","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Set-Location C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace; node inspect_dialog.mjs 2>&1","timeout":20}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":130,"output":259,"cacheRead":110720,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":111109,"cost":{"input":0.000018200000000000002,"output":0.00007252,"cacheRead":0.00310016,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0031908799999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778904383197,"responseId":"12f40a3a-1b27-4d0b-a709-a5280a18d965"}}
