{"type":"message","id":"bb7f4271","parentId":"78e0cb71","timestamp":"2026-05-16T04:06:42.451Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The dialog is present in the HTML but `style=\"display: none\"`. The click didn't trigger it to show, probably because the click event didn't actually trigger the dialog. This could be due to Vue event handling.\n\nLet me try clicking the element differently, or using `page.evaluate` to trigger the click via jQuery/TAPD's internal function.\n\nOr a simpler approach - now that I know the dialog structure (it's an `el-dialog__wrapper`), let me try to interact with it directly by triggering the click via JavaScript.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"弹窗没出现，点击事件可能被 Vue 拦截了。让我用另一种方式触发。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_CkrRK23XkIralbrdm3W22133","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\inspect_vuedialog.mjs","content":"import { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\nconst cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync('tapd_cookies.json','utf8'));\nconst browser = await chromium.launch({headless:true,args:['--no-sandbox','--disable-blink-features=AutomationControlled']});\nconst ctx = await browser.newContext({locale:'zh-CN',viewport:{width:1920,height:1080},userAgent:'Mozilla/5.0...Chrome/125.0.0.0'});\nawait ctx.addCookies(cookies);\nconst page = await ctx.newPage();\nawait page.addInitScript(()=>{delete navigator.webdriver;Object.defineProperty(navigator,'webdriver',{get:()=>false})});\nawait page.goto('https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/prong/stories/add',{waitUntil:'domcontentloaded',timeout:30000}).catch(e=>{});\nawait page.waitForTimeout(5000);\n\n// Try to trigger the dialog via evaluate (using TAPD's JS)\nawait page.evaluate(() => {\n  // Try clicking the edit icon via jQuery if available\n  if (typeof $ !== 'undefined') {\n    $('.j-edit-preset-stories').trigger('click');\n  } else {\n    // Fallback: trigger click event on the element\n    const el = document.querySelector('.j-edit-preset-stories i.font-edit');\n    if (el) {\n      el.dispatchEvent(new MouseEvent('click', {bubbles: true, cancelable: true}));\n    }\n  }\n});\nawait page.waitForTimeout(3000);\n\n// Check the dialog\nconst dialogContent = await page.evaluate(() => {\n  const allHTML = document.body.innerHTML;\n  const idx = allHTML.indexOf('el-dialog__wrapper');\n  if (idx === -1) return 'No dialog found';\n  return allHTML.substring(idx, idx + 3000);\n});\nconsole.log('Dialog HTML:', dialogContent);\n\n// Also check all hidden inputs\nconst presetInputs = await page.evaluate(() => {\n  const inputs = document.querySelectorAll('[name*=\"PresetItems\"], [name*=\"preset\"], [name*=\"create_task\"], [name*=\"auto_succeed\"]');\n  return Array.from(inputs).map(i => ({name: i.name, value: i.value, id: i.id, type: i.type}));\n});\nconsole.log('\\nPreset inputs:', JSON.stringify(presetInputs, null, 2));\n\nawait browser.close();\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":168,"output":758,"cacheRead":111104,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":112030,"cost":{"input":0.000023520000000000002,"output":0.00021224000000000001,"cacheRead":0.003110912,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003346672}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778904395721,"responseId":"f71f9d88-ba03-40dd-b7bf-af6fcff73cff"}}
