{"type":"message","id":"bdcae615","parentId":"8e19e3b5","timestamp":"2026-05-16T04:07:04.222Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The output was truncated. But I can see a key piece of info:\n\n- `data[PresetItems][16][name]` = \"QA\"\n- `data[PresetItems][16][create_task]` = \"false\"\n\nSo the preset items have:\n- index\n- name (e.g., QA)\n- relate_workitem_type_id\n- owner\n- create_task (true/false)\n- etc.\n\nThe `create_task` field determines whether this preset item gets created when the story is created. By default, some are true and some are false.\n\nI need to find which indexes correspond to:\n- 客户端 (Client)\n- QA\n- 策划 (Design)\n\nThen when creating the story, I need to set their `create_task` to \"true\" and all others to \"false\".\n\nLet me get the full list of preset items with their names and create_task values.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"找到了关键信息！预设子工作项有 `create_task` 字段控制是否创建。让我拿到完整列表。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_LFVQodFVpbFp9mQRuuBB2586","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\get_presets.mjs","content":"import { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\nconst cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync('tapd_cookies.json','utf8'));\nconst browser = await chromium.launch({headless:true,args:['--no-sandbox','--disable-blink-features=AutomationControlled']});\nconst ctx = await browser.newContext({locale:'zh-CN',viewport:{width:1920,height:1080},userAgent:'Mozilla/5.0...Chrome/125.0.0.0'});\nawait ctx.addCookies(cookies);\nconst page = await ctx.newPage();\nawait page.addInitScript(()=>{delete navigator.webdriver;Object.defineProperty(navigator,'webdriver',{get:()=>false})});\nawait page.goto('https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/prong/stories/add',{waitUntil:'domcontentloaded',timeout:30000}).catch(e=>{});\nawait page.waitForTimeout(5000);\n\n// Get all PresetItems\nconst presets = await page.evaluate(() => {\n  const items = document.querySelectorAll('input[name*=\"PresetItems\"][name*=\"[name]\"]');\n  const createTasks = document.querySelectorAll('input[name*=\"PresetItems\"][name*=\"[create_task]\"]');\n  const owners = document.querySelectorAll('input[name*=\"PresetItems\"][name*=\"[owner]\"]');\n  \n  const results = [];\n  items.forEach((input, i) => {\n    const idx = input.name.match(/\\[(\\d+)\\]/)?.[1];\n    const createInput = createTasks[i];\n    const ownerInput = owners[i];\n    results.push({\n      index: idx,\n      name: input.value,\n      create_task: createInput?.value || '?',\n      owner: ownerInput?.value || '?'\n    });\n  });\n  return results;\n});\nconsole.log('=== All Preset Items ===');\npresets.forEach(p => console.log(`  [${p.index}] ${p.name} | create: ${p.create_task} | owner: ${p.owner}`));\n\nawait browser.close();\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":839,"output":748,"cacheRead":112384,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":113971,"cost":{"input":0.00011746,"output":0.00020944000000000003,"cacheRead":0.003146752,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0034736520000000002}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778904418111,"responseId":"f9645e0f-5000-4882-b13b-5fbc78e26ffa"}}
