{"type":"message","id":"e3ce391e","parentId":"636ad5bd","timestamp":"2026-05-16T04:07:38.187Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now update the SKILL.md with the Story creation preset rule.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Now update SKILL.md with the Story creation rule."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_kNfDcHOxVb2E2AYpJMSu4205","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\plugin-skills\\tapd-bug-create\\SKILL.md","edits":[{"oldText":"## Create a Story (Requirement)\n\n```javascript\n// URL: https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/prong/stories/add\nawait page.fill('#StoryName', 'Story title');\nawait page.selectOption('#StoryPriority', 'P1');\n// Submit requires dynamically creating a submit input:\nawait page.evaluate(() => {\n  const form = document.querySelector('form');\n  const btn = document.createElement('input');\n  btn.type = 'submit';\n  btn.name = 'data[save_return]';\n  btn.value = '提交&返回';\n  form.appendChild(btn);\n  btn.click();\n});\n```","newText":"## Create a Story (Requirement)\n\n```javascript\nimport { createStory } from './scripts/create_story.mjs';\nawait createStory({ title: '需求标题' });\n```\n\n### Client-side Requirements Rule\n\nFor **客户端 (client-side)** requirements, only 3 preset sub-work items should be created:\n- 客户端 [index 12]\n- 策划 [index 14]\n- QA [index 16]\n\nAll other preset items (UI, 特效, 模型, etc.) should be disabled by setting their `create_task` to `false`.\n\n```javascript\n// In create_story.mjs, this is automatic via CLIENT_PRESET_INDEXES\n// To override: pass custom presetIndexes\nawait createStory({ \n  title: '需求标题',\n  presetIndexes: [12, 14, 16], // 客户端, 策划, QA only\n});\n```\n\n### All 17 Preset Items\n\n| Index | Name | Default Owner |\n|-------|------|---------------|\n| 0 | 原画草稿 | 邝应桥 |\n| 1 | 原画完成稿 | 邝应桥 |\n| 2 | 2D动作 | 江林;王晓松 |\n| 3 | 3D动作 | 樊荣 |\n| 4 | 模型 | 杨学美 |\n| 5 | 特效 | 肖和 |\n| 6 | 特效验收 | 肖和 |\n| 7 | UI | 狄依格 |\n| 8 | UI验收 | 狄依格 |\n| 9 | 动效 | 肖和 |\n| 10 | 动效验收 | 肖和 |\n| 11 | 音频 | 吴美霞;傅一然 |\n| 12 | **客户端** | 王亮亮 |\n| 13 | 服务器 | 黄佳瑞 |\n| 14 | **策划** | 沈嘉琨 |\n| 15 | 文案 | 曹淑琪 |\n| 16 | **QA** | 孙章强 |\n\n### Story Form Fields\n\n| Field | ID | Notes |\n|-------|-----|-------|\n| Title | `#StoryName` | text input |\n| Priority | `#StoryPriority` | select (P0-P3) |\n| Module | `#StoryModule` | select |\n| Version | `#StoryVersion` | select |\n| Handler | `#StoryOwnerValue` | autocomplete: type name |\n| CC | `#StoryCc` (hidden) | format: `姓名;` |\n| Submit | `#btn_save_view` | visible \"创建\" button |\n| Submit & Continue | `#submit_and_continue` | \"提交并继续创建\" |"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":124,"output":931,"cacheRead":116608,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":117663,"cost":{"input":0.00001736,"output":0.00026068,"cacheRead":0.003265024,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0035430640000000003}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778904450625,"responseId":"9dcbe385-adf2-4ad1-b4f8-60958ccc1fd9"}}
