{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6fb4e4bc60b4c2d715a23278e5b\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yousan(叶枝君)\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-05-16 14:11 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yousan(叶枝君) (ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\",\n  \"name\": \"Yousan(叶枝君)\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"3384874a","parentId":"6f168461","timestamp":"2026-05-16T06:11:55.640Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"4e123d78","parentId":"3384874a","timestamp":"2026-05-16T06:12:03.434Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user says the created story still has all 17 preset items enabled, not just the 3 we wanted. So my `page.evaluate` approach of setting the hidden input values didn't work - TAPD probably uses those hidden inputs as initial data and then reads the checkboxes/UI state when submitting, not the hidden value.\n\nIn the dialog I found earlier, the preset items are configured via a Vue dialog that pops up when clicking `.j-edit-preset-stories`. The actual `create_task` checkboxes are probably inside this dialog. I need to:\n\n1. Click the edit button to open the dialog\n2. Uncheck the ones we don't want\n3. Confirm/save the dialog\n\nThe hidden inputs don't directly control the submission - they're just for initialization. TAPD uses the UI state (checkboxes in the dialog) to determine which presets to create.\n\nLet me update the script to:\n1. Open the preset dialog by clicking the edit icon\n2. Find the checkbox for each preset item\n3. Check only the ones we want (客户端, 策划, QA)\n4. Click save/confirm\n5. Then submit the form\n\nLet me first understand the dialog structure. From my earlier inspection, the dialog has:\n- `el-dialog__wrapper` class\n- Contains preset items listed in a table/list\n- Each item has a checkbox\n\nLet me write a script that properly interacts with the dialog.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"看来只改 hidden input 没用，TAPD 提交时读的是对话框里的勾选状态。得实际点开弹窗操作勾选框。让我先看看弹窗里的结构。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_FJf7JwL7ogsbCbx3FfjW5220","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\inspect_preset_dialog.mjs","content":"import { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\nconst cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync('tapd_cookies.json','utf8'));\nconst browser = await chromium.launch({headless:true,args:['--no-sandbox','--disable-blink-features=AutomationControlled']});\nconst ctx = await browser.newContext({locale:'zh-CN',viewport:{width:1920,height:1080},userAgent:'Mozilla/5.0...Chrome/125.0.0.0'});\nawait ctx.addCookies(cookies);\nconst page = await ctx.newPage();\nawait page.addInitScript(()=>{delete navigator.webdriver;Object.defineProperty(navigator,'webdriver',{get:()=>false})});\nawait page.goto('https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/prong/stories/add',{waitUntil:'domcontentloaded',timeout:30000}).catch(e=>{});\nawait page.waitForTimeout(5000);\n\n// Open the dialog by clicking the edit icon\nawait page.evaluate(() => {\n  $('.j-edit-preset-stories').trigger('click');\n});\nawait page.waitForTimeout(3000);\n\n// Now inspect the dialog\nconst dialogHTML = await page.evaluate(() => {\n  const dialog = document.querySelector('.el-dialog__wrapper');\n  if (!dialog) return 'No dialog found';\n  return dialog.outerHTML;\n});\nconsole.log(dialogHTML?.substring(0,5000));\n\nawait browser.close();\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":2818,"output":746,"cacheRead":118400,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":121964,"cost":{"input":0.00039452000000000004,"output":0.00020888000000000002,"cacheRead":0.0033152,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0039185999999999995}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778911915640,"responseId":"de6d1bad-297e-426d-89e3-307deaaf0eeb"}}
