{"type":"message","id":"4f9be551","parentId":"0857b553","timestamp":"2026-05-16T06:12:53.847Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_ET_Jim1YnSblDSViBaAfNYB5323","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[\n  \"jQuery events: click\",\n  \"onclick: none\",\n  \"Child __vue__: no\"\n]\n\nVue component: {\n  \"html\": \"<div class=\\\"fe-vue-component\\\"><div class=\\\"quickly-started-guide\\\" style=\\\"display: none;\\\"><!----><div class=\\\"quickly-started-guide-btn\\\"> 快速上手TAPD <span class=\\\"num\\\">1/4</span><i class=\\\"tapd-icon-close-v2 close-btn\\\"></i></div></div><div class=\\\"el-dialog__wrapper\\\" width=\\\"962px\\\" style=\\\"display: none;\\\"><div role=\\\"dialog\\\" aria-modal=\\\"true\\\" aria-label=\\\"dialog\\\" class=\\\"el-dialog agi-dialog agi-dialog--small agi-dialog--no-footer video-dialog\\\" style=\\\"margin-top: 15vh; width: 962px;\\\"><div class=\\\"el-dialog__h\",\n  \"siblings\": \"\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\\"fe-vue-component\\\"><div class=\\\"quickly-started-guide\\\" style=\\\"display: none;\\\"><!----><div class=\\\"quickly-started-guide-btn\\\"> 快速上手TAPD <span class=\\\"num\\\">1/4</span><i class=\\\"tapd-icon-close-v2 close-btn\\\"></i></div></div><div class=\\\"el-dialog__wrapper\\\" width=\\\"962px\\\" style=\\\"display: none;\\\"><div role=\\\"dialog\\\" aria-modal=\\\"true\\\" aria-label=\\\"dialog\\\" class=\\\"el-dialog agi-dialog agi-dialog--small agi-dialog--no-footer video-dialog\\\" style=\\\"margin-top: 15vh; width: 962px;\\\"><div class=\\\"el-dia\"\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":7231,"aggregated":"[\n  \"jQuery events: click\",\n  \"onclick: none\",\n  \"Child __vue__: no\"\n]\n\nVue component: {\n  \"html\": \"<div class=\\\"fe-vue-component\\\"><div class=\\\"quickly-started-guide\\\" style=\\\"display: none;\\\"><!----><div class=\\\"quickly-started-guide-btn\\\"> 快速上手TAPD <span class=\\\"num\\\">1/4</span><i class=\\\"tapd-icon-close-v2 close-btn\\\"></i></div></div><div class=\\\"el-dialog__wrapper\\\" width=\\\"962px\\\" style=\\\"display: none;\\\"><div role=\\\"dialog\\\" aria-modal=\\\"true\\\" aria-label=\\\"dialog\\\" class=\\\"el-dialog agi-dialog agi-dialog--small agi-dialog--no-footer video-dialog\\\" style=\\\"margin-top: 15vh; width: 962px;\\\"><div class=\\\"el-dialog__h\",\n  \"siblings\": \"\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\\"fe-vue-component\\\"><div class=\\\"quickly-started-guide\\\" style=\\\"display: none;\\\"><!----><div class=\\\"quickly-started-guide-btn\\\"> 快速上手TAPD <span class=\\\"num\\\">1/4</span><i class=\\\"tapd-icon-close-v2 close-btn\\\"></i></div></div><div class=\\\"el-dialog__wrapper\\\" width=\\\"962px\\\" style=\\\"display: none;\\\"><div role=\\\"dialog\\\" aria-modal=\\\"true\\\" aria-label=\\\"dialog\\\" class=\\\"el-dialog agi-dialog agi-dialog--small agi-dialog--no-footer video-dialog\\\" style=\\\"margin-top: 15vh; width: 962px;\\\"><div class=\\\"el-dia\"\n}","cwd":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778911973847}}
{"type":"message","id":"a65b4d34","parentId":"4f9be551","timestamp":"2026-05-16T06:13:01.584Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Interesting findings:\n1. The `.j-edit-preset-stories` element has a **jQuery click event** bound to it! So it uses jQuery to handle the click.\n2. The dialog is a Vue component (Element UI `el-dialog`) but initially `display: none`\n\nSince it uses jQuery, I can trigger the click via:\n```javascript\n// Trigger the jQuery click handler directly\nconst el = document.querySelector('.j-edit-preset-stories');\n$(el).trigger('click');\n```\n\nOr I can try Playwright's click with dispatchEvent to trigger the jQuery handler.\n\nWait, but my earlier `click({force: true})` should have triggered a click event on the element. The jQuery handler should have fired. Unless the event isn't propagating to jQuery because Playwright's synthetic click uses a different mechanism.\n\nLet me try using `page.dispatchEvent()` or triggering the click event directly via `page.evaluate`.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"找到原因了——元素绑的是 jQuery 事件，Playwright 的 click 没触发上去。直接用 evaluate 触发。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_TgUCAu9kgXgmf7usLAOi5619","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\trigger_dialog.mjs","content":"import { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\nconst cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync('tapd_cookies.json','utf8'));\nconst browser = await chromium.launch({headless:true,args:['--no-sandbox','--disable-blink-features=AutomationControlled']});\nconst ctx = await browser.newContext({locale:'zh-CN',viewport:{width:1920,height:1080},userAgent:'Mozilla/5.0...Chrome/125.0.0.0'});\nawait ctx.addCookies(cookies);\nconst page = await ctx.newPage();\nawait page.addInitScript(()=>{delete navigator.webdriver;Object.defineProperty(navigator,'webdriver',{get:()=>false})});\nawait page.goto('https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/prong/stories/add',{waitUntil:'domcontentloaded',timeout:30000}).catch(e=>{});\nawait page.waitForTimeout(5000);\n\n// Use dispatchEvent to trigger the jQuery handler\nawait page.evaluate(() => {\n  const el = document.querySelector('.j-edit-preset-stories');\n  if (el) {\n    el.dispatchEvent(new Event('click', {bubbles: true, cancelable: true}));\n  }\n});\nawait page.waitForTimeout(3000);\n\n// Check dialog visibility and content\nconst result = await page.evaluate(() => {\n  const dialog = document.querySelector('.el-dialog__wrapper');\n  if (!dialog) return 'No dialog';\n  const visible = dialog.style.display !== 'none';\n  if (!visible) return 'Dialog display:none';\n  // Dialog is visible - get its contents\n  return dialog.textContent?.trim().substring(0,1000) || 'Empty dialog';\n});\nconsole.log('Dialog result:', result);\n\n// Also try with jQuery trigger\nawait page.evaluate(() => {\n  const el = document.querySelector('.j-edit-preset-stories');\n  if (el && typeof $ !== 'undefined') {\n    $(el).trigger('click');\n  }\n});\nawait page.waitForTimeout(3000);\n\nconst result2 = await page.evaluate(() => {\n  const dialog = document.querySelector('.el-dialog__wrapper');\n  if (!dialog) return 'No dialog';\n  return {style: dialog.getAttribute('style'), text: dialog.textContent?.trim().substring(0,500)};\n});\nconsole.log('After jQuery trigger:', JSON.stringify(result2));\n\nawait browser.close();\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":396,"output":829,"cacheRead":124032,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":125257,"cost":{"input":0.000055440000000000005,"output":0.00023212000000000002,"cacheRead":0.003472896,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003760456}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778911973849,"responseId":"101ca6f5-0359-45a0-b2e0-ec47634ca5d6"}}
