{"type":"message","id":"3800f0ce","parentId":"c5f220ec","timestamp":"2026-05-16T06:14:59.626Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Excellent! I found several global functions:\n- `isLoadPresetWorkitemTree` - boolean for load state\n- `PresetTaskDialog` - This is likely the dialog function!\n- `getPresetWorkitemHelpers` - Helper functions\n- `presetWorkitemsHelper` - The helper object\n- `presetWorkitemsHelper` might have a `show` or `open` method\n\nLet me check what `PresetTaskDialog` and `presetWorkitemsHelper` do.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"找到了！`PresetTaskDialog` 和 `presetWorkitemsHelper` 是全局函数。让我看看怎么调用。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_4AHPPq2XixS2Gc6WlL4k3176","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Set-Location C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace; node -e \"\nimport { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\nconst c = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync('tapd_cookies.json','utf8'));\nconst b = await chromium.launch({headless:true,args:['--no-sandbox','--disable-blink-features=AutomationControlled']});\nconst ctx = await b.newContext({locale:'zh-CN',viewport:{width:1920,height:1080},userAgent:'Mozilla/5.0...Chrome/125.0.0.0'});\nawait ctx.addCookies(c);\nconst p = await ctx.newPage();\nawait p.addInitScript(()=>{delete navigator.webdriver;});\nawait p.goto('https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/prong/stories/add',{waitUntil:'domcontentloaded',timeout:30000}).catch(e=>{});\nawait p.waitForTimeout(5000);\n\nconst info = await p.evaluate(() => {\n  const result = {};\n  \n  // Check PresetTaskDialog\n  if (typeof PresetTaskDialog === 'function') {\n    result.PresetTaskDialog = PresetTaskDialog.toString().substring(0,500);\n  } else if (PresetTaskDialog) {\n    result.PresetTaskDialog = 'non-function: ' + typeof PresetTaskDialog;\n  } else {\n    result.PresetTaskDialog = 'null/undefined';\n  }\n  \n  // Check getPresetWorkitemHelpers\n  if (typeof getPresetWorkitemHelpers === 'function') {\n    const helpers = getPresetWorkitemHelpers();\n    result.helpersType = typeof helpers;\n    if (helpers && typeof helpers === 'object') {\n      result.helperKeys = Object.keys(helpers);\n      helpers.forEach((h, i) => {\n        if (i < 5 && typeof h === 'function') {\n          result['helper_' + i] = h.toString().substring(0,200);\n        }\n      });\n    }\n  }\n  \n  // Check presetWorkitemsHelper  \n  if (presetWorkitemsHelper && typeof presetWorkitemsHelper === 'object') {\n    result.presetWorkitemsHelperKeys = Object.keys(presetWorkitemsHelper);\n    Object.keys(presetWorkitemsHelper).forEach(k => {\n      const v = presetWorkitemsHelper[k];\n      if (typeof v === 'function') {\n        result['helper_' + k] = v.toString().substring(0,300);\n      } else {\n        result['helper_' + k] = typeof v + ': ' + JSON.stringify(v).substring(0,100);\n      }\n    });\n  }\n  \n  return result;\n});\nconsole.log(JSON.stringify(info,null,2));\nawait b.close();\n\" 2>&1","timeout":20}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":278,"output":796,"cacheRead":131328,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":132402,"cost":{"input":0.00003892,"output":0.00022288,"cacheRead":0.003677184,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003938984}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778912093055,"responseId":"c3c78bf2-3cf7-4106-9f61-1b1786f89d6b"}}
