{"type":"message","id":"f43e2026","parentId":"ff603cbc","timestamp":"2026-05-16T06:15:54.624Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Excellent! I found it! `PresetTaskDialog` has a `showDialog()` method that opens the dialog!\n\nLooking at the `init` function:\n```javascript\n$(\".j-edit-preset-stories\").click(function() {\n    return i.showDialog(e), !1\n});\n```\n\nSo clicking `.j-edit-preset-stories` calls `PresetTaskDialog.showDialog()`. But Playwright's click wasn't triggering the jQuery handler. Let me try calling `PresetTaskDialog.showDialog()` directly!\n\nAnd after the dialog is shown, I can interact with the checkboxes and save.\n\nBut wait, I also need to understand what the dialog contains. Let me:\n1. Call `PresetTaskDialog.showDialog()` to open it\n2. Inspect the dialog for checkboxes\n3. Uncheck/check the right ones\n4. Save\n\nLet me also look at the dialog content. The `showDialog` creates a dialog using `window.uiDialogTitlebar` or similar. The dialog has a `#preset-tasks-editform` template that contains the preset items as checkboxes.\n\nLet me write a script to:\n1. Open the page\n2. Fill the basic fields\n3. Call `PresetTaskDialog.showDialog()` directly\n4. Wait for the dialog\n5. Check/uncheck presets\n6. Save dialog\n7. Submit form","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"找到了！`PresetTaskDialog.showDialog()` 可以直接打开弹窗。让我走通完整流程。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_52ZJ0CqqiF6C466afpeb0795","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\test_full_preset.mjs","content":"import { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\nconst cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync('tapd_cookies.json','utf8'));\nconst browser = await chromium.launch({headless:true,args:['--no-sandbox','--disable-blink-features=AutomationControlled']});\nconst ctx = await browser.newContext({locale:'zh-CN',viewport:{width:1920,height:1080},userAgent:'Mozilla/5.0...Chrome/125.0.0.0'});\nawait ctx.addCookies(cookies);\nconst page = await ctx.newPage();\nawait page.addInitScript(()=>{delete navigator.webdriver;Object.defineProperty(navigator,'webdriver',{get:()=>false})});\nawait page.goto('https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/prong/stories/add',{waitUntil:'domcontentloaded',timeout:30000}).catch(e=>{});\nawait page.waitForTimeout(5000);\n\n// Fill basic fields\nawait page.fill('#StoryName', 'test-preset-dialog');\nawait page.selectOption('#StoryPriority', 'P2');\nawait page.selectOption('#StoryVersion', '【1V1】正式版本V2.0');\n\n// Open the preset dialog directly via JS\nawait page.evaluate(() => {\n  if (typeof PresetTaskDialog !== 'undefined' && PresetTaskDialog.showDialog) {\n    PresetTaskDialog.showDialog();\n  } else {\n    // Fallback: trigger jQuery click\n    $('.j-edit-preset-stories').trigger('click');\n  }\n});\nawait page.waitForTimeout(3000);\n\n// Check dialog state and find preset checkboxes\nconst dialogInfo = await page.evaluate(() => {\n  const r = {};\n  // Find visible dialog\n  const dialogs = document.querySelectorAll('.ui-dialog, .el-dialog__wrapper');\n  dialogs.forEach((d, i) => {\n    const style = d.getAttribute('style') || '';\n    const text = d.textContent?.trim().substring(0,500) || '';\n    r['dialog_' + i] = {style: style.substring(0,100), text: text.substring(0,300)};\n  });\n  \n  // Check checkboxes in the dialog\n  const checkboxes = document.querySelectorAll('.ui-dialog:visible input[type=checkbox], .el-dialog__wrapper:not([style*=\\\"display: none\\\"]) input[type=checkbox]');\n  r.checkboxCount = checkboxes.length;\n  r.checkboxes = Array.from(checkboxes).slice(0,25).map(cb => ({\n    id: cb.id,\n    name: cb.name,\n    value: cb.value,\n    checked: cb.checked,\n    visible: cb.offsetParent !== null\n  }));\n  \n  return r;\n});\nconsole.log('Dialog state:', JSON.stringify(dialogInfo, null, 2));\n\n// Take screenshot to review\nawait page.screenshot({path:'preset_dialog_opened.png'});\n\nawait browser.close();\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1053,"output":1040,"cacheRead":135040,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":137133,"cost":{"input":0.00014742000000000002,"output":0.00029120000000000003,"cacheRead":0.00378112,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00421974}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778912145874,"responseId":"03033572-067b-4ef5-8b4b-7df8cbb86c80"}}
