{"type":"message","id":"cf9e2cc5","parentId":"6997b03f","timestamp":"2026-05-16T06:17:31.224Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the structure! Each row has:\n1. Row div with `idx=\"0\"` (index 0-16)\n2. A workitem type select with dropdown\n3. An input with value \"原画草稿\" (etc.)\n4. But NO create_task checkbox!\n\nThe rows all have `style=\"display: flex;\"` which means they're all visible. In the dialog, the items seem to be either:\n- Included (shown as rows) or \n- Not included (deleted via `.j-remove-row` icon)\n\nThere's NO checkbox to determine whether to create the preset or not. Instead, the dialog uses a different mechanism:\n- Each row IS a preset item\n- To remove a preset, you click the `.j-remove-row` (X) button\n- When you click \"提交\" (submit) in the dialog, it updates the form's data\n\nSo the approach should be:\n1. Open the dialog\n2. Find the rows for items we DON'T want (all except 客户端, 策划, QA)\n3. Click the `.j-remove-row` (X) button on each unwanted row\n4. Click \"提交\" to save the dialog\n5. Then submit the form\n\nLet me verify this by checking the full dialog HTML to see if there are any \"create_task\" related elements.\n\nActually, let me also check - there might be a `j-row-cell--visible` checkbox or something that controls visibility. Let me look at the other parts of each row.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_Nd6SyQHiIADiJcXQT5ys3885","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Set-Location C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace; Select-String -Path dialog_html.txt -Pattern \"visible|display|delete|remove|create_task\" 2>&1 | Select -First 20"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":478,"output":411,"cacheRead":144000,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":144889,"cost":{"input":0.00006692,"output":0.00011508,"cacheRead":0.004032,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004214}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":