          \\\"id\\\": \\\"call_00_ET_i7l01hxT59kb3b\r\nRtgd5h1056\\\",\\n          \\\"name\\\": \\\"process\\\",\\n          \\\"arguments\\\": {\\n            \\\"sessionId\\\": \\\"salty-mist\\\",\r\n\\n            \\\"timeout\\\": 20000,\\n            \\\"action\\\": \\\"poll\\\"\\n          }\\n        }\\n      ],\\n      \\\"api\\\": \\\r\n\"openai-completions\\\",\\n      \\\"provider\\\": \\\"deepseek\\\",\\n      \\\"model\\\": \\\"deepseek-v4-flash\\\",\\n      \\\"stopReason\\\r\n\": \\\"toolUse\\\",\\n      \\\"timestamp\\\": 1778912026913,\\n      \\\"responseId\\\": \\\"b1bf3d5e-0208-47dc-b4a1-ea5632c690f9\\\",\\n\r\n      \\\"__openclaw\\\": {\\n        \\\"id\\\": \\\"f4f5d642\\\",\\n        \\\"seq\\\": 350\\n      }\\n    },\\n    {\\n      \\\"role\\\": \\\r\n\"assistant\\\",\\n      \\\"content\\\": [\\n        {\\n          \\\"type\\\": \\\"thinking\\\",\\n          \\\"thinking\\\": \\\"No POST re\r\nquests were captured, meaning the page navigated before any POST was intercepted, or the form submission used a differe\r\nnt mechanism (like an AJAX call that went through before the listener was set up).\\\\n\\\\nWait, the page.on('request') sh\r\nould work for all requests. Maybe the form submit didn't include create_task parameters because an AJAX call or somethi\r\nng else handled the save.\\\\n\\\\nActually, looking at the result - no POST requests at all were captured from tapd.cn pat\r\nhs that include create_task. This might mean the form submission uses a standard form POST (which causes navigation), a\r\nnd Playwright's page.on('request') only captures XHR/fetch requests, not form navigations.\\\\n\\\\nAlso, the auto_succeed_\r\nstory_fields was empty (\\\\\\\"no field\\\\\\\"), which means the hidden input existed but had no value.\\\\n\\\\nLet me try a dif\r\nferent approach - instead of intercepting, let me try to actually trigger the dialog. Let me look at what JavaScript fi\r\nle handles the click on `.j-edit-preset-stories`.\\\\n\\\\nActually, I think the key is `vueComponentConnect`. This library\r\n connects static HTML elements to Vue components. The `.j-edit-preset-stories` probably triggers a Vue component method\r\n via `vueComponentConnect`. Let me look for how to call it.\\\\n\\\\nActually, let me try yet another approach. Instead of \r\ntrying to open the dialog, let me directly modify the form data right before submission by overriding the form's submit\r\n handler.\\\"\\n        },\\n        {\\n          \\\"type\\\": \\\"text\\\",\\n          \\\"text\\\": \\\"让我尝试另一种方式——在表单提交\r\n前直接拦截并修改 preset 数据。\\\"\\n        },\\n        {\\n          \\\"type\\\": \\\"toolCall\\\",\\n          \\\"id\\\": \\\"call_00_\r\nzgwA3BvZ0G48pDijsX4P3879\\\",\\n          \\\"name\\\": \\\"write\\\",\\n          \\\"arguments\\\": {\\n            \\\"path\\\": \\\"C:\\\\\\\\\r\nUsers\\\\\\\\yyzypublic\\\\\\\\.openclaw\\\\\\\\workspace\\\\\\\\test_preset_override.mjs\\\",\\n            \\\"content\\\": \\\"import { chrom\r\nium } from 'playwright';\\\\nimport fs from 'fs';\\\\nconst cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync('tapd_cookies.json','utf8'\r\n));\\\\nconst browser = await chromium.launch({headless:true,args:['--no-sandbox','--disable-blink-features=AutomationCon\r\ntrolled']});\\\\nconst ctx = await browser.newContext({locale:'zh-CN',viewport:{width:1920,height:1080},userAgent:'Mozill\r\na/5.0...Chrome/125.0.0.0'});\\\\nawait ctx.addCookies(cookies);\\\\nconst page = await ctx.newPage();\\\\nawait page.addInitS\r\ncript(()=>{delete navigator.webdriver;Object.defineProperty(navigator,'webdriver',{get:()=>false})});\\\\n\\\\n// Intercept\r\n form action\\\\nlet intercepted = false;\\\\npage.on('request', req => {\\\\n  if (req.method() === 'POST' && req.url().incl\r\nudes('/stories/save')) {\\\\n    const data = req.postData() || '';\\\\n    console.log('=== POST data intercepted ===');\\\\\r\nn    console.log(data);\\\\n    intercepted = true;\\\\n  }\\\\n});\\\\n\\\\nawait page.goto('https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/prong/\r\nstories/add',{waitUntil:'domcontentloaded',timeout:30000}).catch(e=>{});\\\\nawait page.waitForTimeout(5000);\\\\n\\\\n// Fil\r\nl form\\\\nawait page.fill('#StoryName', 'test-preset-2');\\\\nawait page.selectOption('#StoryPriority', 'P2');\\\\nawait pag\r\ne.selectOption('#StoryVersion', '【1V1】正式版本V2.0');\\\\n\\\\n// Override form submit handler to inject preset data  \\\\naw\r\nait page.evaluate(() => {\\\\n  // Before form submit, set correct preset values\\\\n  const form = document.querySelector(\r\n'form');\\\\n  if (!form) return;\\\\n  \\\\n  form.addEventListener('submit', function(e) {\\\\n    const tasks = document.que\r\nrySelectorAll('input[name*=\\\\\\\"PresetItems\\\\\\\"][name*=\\\\\\\"[create_task]\\\\\\\"]');\\\\n    tasks.forEach(input => {\\\\n      \r\nconst match = input.name.match(/\\\\\\\\[(\\\\\\\\d+)\\\\\\\\]/);\\\\n      if (match) {\\\\n        const idx = parseInt(match[1]);\\\\n\r\n        // Only keep 12(客户端), 14(策划), 16(QA)\\\\n        input.value = [12, 14, 16].includes(idx) ? 'true' : 'false'\r\n;\\\\n      }\\\\n    });\\\\n    console.log('Submit handler fired, presets modified');\\\\n  }, true); // useCapture to fire \r\nbefore other handlers\\\\n});\\\\n\\\\n// Submit\\\\nawait page.click('#btn_save_view');\\\\nawait page.waitForTimeout(8000);\\\\n\\\r\n\\nif (!intercepted) {\\\\n  console.log('\\\\\\\\nNo POST intercepted - checking page state...');\\\\n  console.log('Current UR\r\nL:', page.url());\\\\n  // Check if page navigated\\\\n  try {\\\\n    const errors = await page.evaluate(() => {\\\\n      ret\r\nurn Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('.error,[class*=error]')).map(e=>e.textContent?.trim()).filter(Boolean);\\\\n   \r\n });\\\\n    console.log('Errors:', errors.join(', ') || 'none');\\\\n  } catch(e) {\\\\n    console.log('Page ctx destroyed \r\n(navigation)');\\\\n  }\\\\n}\\\\n\\\\nawait browser.close();\\\\n\\\"\\n          }\\n        }\\n      ],\\n      \\\"api\\\": \\\"openai-c\r\nompletions\\\",\\n      \\\"provider\\\": \\\"deepseek\\\",\\n      \\\"model\\\": \\\"deepseek-v4-flash\\\",\\n      \\\"stopReason\\\": \\\"tool\r\nUse\\\",\\n      \\\"timestamp\\\": 1778912029361,\\n      \\\"responseId\\\": \\\"bab6ec87-e2aa-4e0c-a7cd-37ec1e976fba\\\",\\n      \\\"_\r\n_openclaw\\\": {\\n        \\\"id\\\": \\\"c79c9b01\\\",\\n        \\\"seq\\\": 352\\n      }\\n    },\\n    {\\n      \\\"role\\\": \\\"assistan\r\nt\\\",\\n      \\\"content\\\": [\\n        {\\n          \\\"type\\\": \\\"toolCall\\\",\\n          \\\"id\\\": \\\"call_00_ET_5BPf3DERA6ZRZk\r\nuTt9HX2913\\\",\\n          \\\"name\\\": \\\"exec\\\",\\n          \\\"arguments\\\": {\\n            \\\"command\\\": \\\"Set-Location C:\\\\\\\r\n\\Users\\\\\\\\yyzypublic\\\\\\\\.openclaw\\\\\\\\workspace; node test_preset_override.mjs 2>&1\\\",\\n            \\\"timeout\\\": 25\\n   \r\n       }\\n        }\\n      ],\\n      \\\"api\\\": \\\"openai-completions\\\",\\n      \\\"provider\\\": \\\"deepseek\\\",\\n      \\\"model\r\n\\\": \\\"deepseek-v4-flash\\\",\\n      \\\"stopReason\\\": \\\"toolUse\\\",\\n      \\\"timestamp\\\": 1778912040060,\\n      \\\"responseId\r\n\\\": \\\"6fa9a943-b198-4df6-8182-412625e5e8fc\\\",\\n      \\\"__openclaw\\\": {\\n        \\\"id\\\": \\\"dd7cd698\\\",\\n        \\\"seq\\\":\r\n 354\\n      }\\n    },\\n    {\\n      \\\"role\\\": \\\"assistant\\\",\\n      \\\"content\\\": [\\n        {\\n          \\\"type\\\": \\\"to\r\n\n⚠️ [... middle content omitted — showing head and tail ...]\n\n     \\\"arguments\\\": {\\n            \\\"sessionKey\\\": \\\"agent:main:feishu:direct:ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\\\",\\n \r\n           \\\"limit\\\": 200,\\n            \\\"includeTools\\\": false\\n          }\\n        }\\n      ],\\n      \\\"api\\\": \\\"ope\r\nnai-completions\\\",\\n      \\\"provider\\\": \\\"deepseek\\\",\\n      \\\"model\\\": \\\"deepseek-v4-flash\\\",\\n      \\\"stopReason\\\": \\\r\n\"toolUse\\\",\\n      \\\"timestamp\\\": 1778926701165,\\n      \\\"responseId\\\": \\\"c40d4225-9af1-499e-b6b7-195aa13d979c\\\",\\n    \r\n  \\\"__openclaw\\\": {\\n        \\\"id\\\": \\\"22c21728\\\",\\n        \\\"seq\\\": 448\\n      }\\n    }\\n  ],\\n  \\\"truncated\\\": true,\\\r\nn  \\\"droppedMessages\\\": true,\\n  \\\"contentTruncated\\\": true,\\n  \\\"contentRedacted\\\": false,\\n  \\\"bytes\\\": 81895\\n}[... \r\n77937 more characters truncated]\"}],\"details\":{\"persistedDetailsTruncated\":true,\"originalDetailsBytesAtLeast\":8199,\"ori\r\nginalDetailKeys\":[\"sessionKey\",\"messages\",\"truncated\",\"droppedMessages\",\"contentTruncated\",\"contentRedacted\",\"bytes\"],\"\r\ntruncated\":true},\"isError\":false,\"timestamp\":1778926706086}}\r\nC:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\agents\\main\\sessions\\3b440681-8d44-4880-b22a-e550bbd9c908.jsonl:480:{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\r\n\":\"c8f3cfae\",\"parentId\":\"e982b124\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-05-16T10:18:34.285Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"ty\r\npe\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"Looking at the session history, the content is truncated/summarized. I can see the messages \r\nbut the actual interactive card content from yesterday isn't preserved in the text history.\\n\\nThe user replied to a me\r\nssage that contained an \\\"[Interactive Card]\\\" which I sent yesterday. They want me to \\\"发一下\\\" (send again/repost) t\r\nhe 7 requirement templates.\\n\\nSince I can't see the card content from the history, I need to try another approach. The\r\n card was about \\\"7个需求模版\\\" - let me think about what this could be in the context of TAPD and the monthly night ga\r\nme project.\\n\\nLooking at the SKILL.md I updated, in the preset items table I documented 17 preset items. But the user \r\nspecifically says \\\"7个需求模版\\\" - 7 requirement templates.\\n\\nIn TAPD, these are likely different template types for \r\ncreating requirements/stories. The workspace might have 7 different templates for different types of requirements.\\n\\nI\r\n'm guessing here, but the 7 requirement templates might refer to different Story templates or work item types in the 月\r\n圆之夜 workspace. Maybe things like:\\n1. 客户端需求\\n2. 策划需求\\n3. UI需求\\n4. 等等\\n\\nBut without the actual card con\r\ntent, I can't be sure. Let me ask the user what the 7 templates are, or try to look at the TAPD workspace directly for \r\ntemplate information.\\n\\nActually, the user replied saying \\\"这个\\\" (this) pointing to the interactive card. They want \r\nme to repost that card content. Since the card was something I sent yesterday, maybe I can generate it again from my kn\r\nowledge. The \\\"7个需求模版\\\" was likely a summary or template reference that I compiled for the user.\\n\\nLet me check o\r\nne more thing - the message ID that was replied to: `om_x100b6f47a1d62820b3fd1d75eda3081`. Let me search for this exact\r\n ID elsewhere.\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning_content\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"我找到了昨天交互卡片的线索。让我查看引用\r\n消息的具体内容。\"},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"call_00_An2QVKHU90KsUN1O3VCv0903\",\"name\":\"exec\",\"arguments\":{\"command\":\"Set-\r\nLocation C:\\\\Users\\\\yyzypublic\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace; Select-String -Path \\\"C:\\\\Users\\\\yyzypublic\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents\\\\m\r\nain\\\\sessions\\\\3b440681-8d44-4880-b22a-e550bbd9c908.jsonl\\\" -Pattern \\\"om_x100b6f47a1d62820b3fd1d75eda3081\\\" 2>&1\"}}],\"\r\napi\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"deepseek\",\"model\":\"deepseek-v4-flash\",\"usage\":{\"input\":28183,\"output\":562,\"cacheR\r\nead\":169856,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":198601,\"cost\":{\"input\":0.00394562,\"output\":0.00015736,\"cacheRead\":0.004755968,\r\n\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0.008858948}},\"stopReason\":\"toolUse\",\"timestamp\":1778926706090,\"responseId\":\"53e1ab3b-3a62-465a-\r\nba8f-924d849ea070\"}}[... 9571 more characters truncated]"}],"details":{"persistedDetailsTruncated":true,"originalDetailsBytesAtLeast":8193,"originalDetailKeys":["status","exitCode","d