{"type":"message","id":"d7bd4211","parentId":"e06e5c13","timestamp":"2026-05-16T10:36:03.155Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"已存好！现在脚本支持4种1V1需求模板了：\n\n```javascript\n// 客户端开单（默认）→ 客户端、QA、策划\ncreateStory({ title: 'xxx' })\n// or\ncreateStory({ title: 'xxx', template: 'client' })\n\n// 服务端开单 → 服务端、QA、策划  \ncreateStory({ title: 'xxx', template: 'server' })\n\n// 策划需求单 → 策划、QA、客户端、服务端\ncreateStory({ title: 'xxx', template: 'design' })\n\n// UI需求单 → UI、UI验收、客户端、策划、QA\ncreateStory({ title: 'xxx', template: 'ui' })\n```\n\n预设处理人也自动配好了。以后喊我开单直接说「开个UI需求单叫xxx」就行 😎"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":118,"output":178,"cacheRead":181248,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":181544,"cost":{"input":0.00001652,"output":0.000049840000000000004,"cacheRead":0.005074944,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.005141303999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778927759282,"responseId":"5546f29f-5cef-4d74-8af1-4b905e188685"}}
