{"type":"message","id":"9365a1a5","parentId":"6f65dc40","timestamp":"2026-05-16T11:27:52.671Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to add 2 more templates:\n1. 动作需求单 - for 动效/动作 related requirements\n2. 音频需求单 - for 音频 related requirements\n\nThey said \"跟客户端的单子差不多\" - similar to the client template. So these would follow the same pattern:\n- 动作需求单 → 动作相关 preset items + QA + 策划\n- 音频需求单 → 音频 related preset items + QA + 策划\n\nLooking at the preset items:\n- 动作 related: [2] 2D动作, [3] 3D动作, [9] 动效, [10] 动效验收\n- 音频 related: [11] 音频\n\nWait, \"动作\" could mean:\n- [2] 2D动作\n- [3] 3D动作\n- [9] 动效\n- [10] 动效验收\n\nThese are separate items. Maybe the 动作需求单 should include some combination of these.\n\nAnd 音频 is just [11] 音频.\n\nBut \"跟客户端的单子差不多\" means similar structure - so maybe:\n- 动作需求单 → [2]2D动作, [3]3D动作, [9]动效, [10]动效验收, [16]QA, [14]策划\n- 音频需求单 → [11]音频, [16]QA, [14]策划\n\nActually, I'm not sure about the handler/owner. For 动作, who is the handler? Looking at the default owners:\n- 2D动作: 江林;王晓松;\n- 3D动作: 樊荣;\n- 动效: 肖和;\n- 动效验收: 肖和;\n\nFor 音频:\n- 音频: 吴美霞;傅一然;\n\nThe user said \"跟客户端的单子差不多\" - similar structure. For 客户端 template, the handler is 叶枝君 (the person responsible for that area). So for 动作, the handler would be someone who handles 动作 work, and for 音频, the handler would be someone who handles 音频.\n\nBut I don't know who those people are offhand. Let me just add the templates with the preset items and ask the user who the handlers should be.\n\nActually, thinking about it more practically - the user wants to be able to create these templates. Let me add them and ask about the handlers.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好，先加上这两个模板。不过需要确认一下处理人。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_j8DQpaRrI21qlU1GwT8x2558","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\create_story.mjs","edits":[{"oldText":"  ui: {  // 1V1UI需求单模版\n    name: 'UI需求单',\n    keepIndexes: [7, 8, 12, 