{"type":"message","id":"f92e49fd","parentId":"1a6ecb02","timestamp":"2026-05-16T12:03:52.640Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user just wants me to confirm that the info is recorded. It already is - I've updated:\n1. create_story.mjs with all 6 templates\n2. SKILL.md with the template table\n3. MEMORY.md with the summary\n\nLet me do a final save of MEMORY.md to make sure everything is consistent.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"已经全记好啦，总结一下现在保存的内容：\n\n**📄 `create_story.mjs`** — 6种模板自动化脚本\n**📄 SKILL.md** — 完整模板配置表 + 用法\n**📄 MEMORY.md** — 简要记录\n\n```\nTEMPLATES = {\n  client:  客户端 + QA + 策划           → 叶枝君\n  server:  服务端 + QA + 策划           → 陈霄豪\n  design:  策划 + QA + 客户端 + 服务端   → 赵乾\n  ui:      UI + UI验收 + 客户端 + 策划 + QA → 小冰\n  motion:  2D动作 + 3D动作 + 动效 + 动效验收 + 策划 + QA → 肖和\n  audio:   音频 + 策划 + QA             → 吴美霞\n}\n```\n\n随时可以开单，一句「开个XX需求单叫xxx」即可 😎"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":21752,"output":280,"cacheRead":163840,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":185872,"cost":{"input":0.00304528,"output":0.00007840000000000001,"cacheRead":0.0045875199999999994,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0077112}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778933027450,"responseId":"e27deceb-672f-4c78-86fb-27f1298890c3"}}
